<programme start="20241220041500 +0000" stop="20241220050000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.ee"><title lang="ee">Pit Bulls &amp; Parolees</title><desc lang="ee">American reality series following the team at the Villalobos Rescue centre on their quest to rescue and rehome dogs. Founded by Tia Maria Torres, the centre challenges the misconceptions surrounding &apos;bully breeds&apos;, such as pit bulls, with hopes of eventually rehoming them. Alongside Tia are her team of dog-loving parolees, each tasked with training, rescuing and caring for the animals. Each episode covers the emotional stories of both her employees and their rescue dogs. Will their jobs help them as they transition away from jail or will they struggle alongside the pups to rebuild their reputation?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220055000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.ee"><title lang="ee">My Cat from Hell</title><desc lang="ee">Jackson Galaxy is a cat behaviorist. He is the person who resolves conflicts or behavioral issues between the owners and their cats or even between the cats and other pets. These are attacks and misbehavior, and Jackson is a true cat-lover and a believer that any problem can be solved thanks to love, patience and proper handling. Taking good care of cats is a demanding process and a whole science, but in return you will get a loving and purring family member.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220055000 +0000" stop="20241220064000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.ee"><title lang="ee">My Cat from Hell</title><desc lang="ee">Jackson Galaxy is a cat behaviorist. He is the person who resolves conflicts or behavioral issues between the owners and their cats or even between the cats and other pets. These are attacks and misbehavior, and Jackson is a true cat-lover and a believer that any problem can be solved thanks to love, patience and proper handling. Taking good care of cats is a demanding process and a whole science, but in return you will get a loving and purring family member.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220064000 +0000" stop="20241220073000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.ee"><title lang="ee">Animal Cops: Philadelphia</title><desc lang="ee">Documentary series that follows the people who work for The Pennsylvania Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals, based in downtown Philadelphia, and whose job is to, on a daily basis, rescue, rehabilitate and re-home unwanted or neglected animals of all types, seeking justice against the perpetrators that abused them. Although, primarily following the Law Enforcement Officers, the programme also shows the combined efforts of PSPCA Veterinarians, Technicians, Shelter Staff and Administration.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220073000 +0000" stop="20241220082500 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.ee"><title lang="ee">Tanked</title><desc lang="ee">Follow aquarium enthusiasts Brett Raymer and Wayde King as they attempt to build some of the most luxurious fish tanks in the world. At Acrylic Tank Manufacturing, the brothers-in-law guide you through the design process and the building of their truly jaw-dropping aquariums. Experience the unveiling of finished tanks housed everywhere from restaurants and banks, to glamorous casinos and mansions. Join the duo in their Las Vegas workshop as they deliver some budget-shattering builds to their high-profile clientele.</desc></programme>
