<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220055000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.lv"><title lang="lv">My Cat from Hell</title><desc lang="lv">Jackson Galaxy is a cat behaviorist. He is the person who resolves conflicts or behavioral issues between the owners and their cats or even between the cats and other pets. These are attacks and misbehavior, and Jackson is a true cat-lover and a believer that any problem can be solved thanks to love, patience and proper handling. Taking good care of cats is a demanding process and a whole science, but in return you will get a loving and purring family member.</desc></programme>
