<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220200000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.lv"><title lang="lv">Legends Of the Wild</title><desc lang="lv">The natural world is full of tales of mysterious animal attacks on humans and inexplicable sightings of strange and sinister creatures. Wilderness experts Damian Duffy and Matt Hoffman decided to check out these stories for themselves and set off across the globe to investigate the reports. Using their experience and skills as a former army paratrooper (Damian) and an accomplished wildife photographer (Matt) they journey deep into the wild places and risk their lives to uncover the truth.Their investigations take them from the baffling and gory deaths of ranchers in Brazil to the return of a mythical Australian killer to the disappearance of villagers and farm animals in the Philippines and mystifying Alaskan sea creatures.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220200000 +0000" stop="20241220210000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.lv"><title lang="lv">Legends Of the Wild</title><desc lang="lv">The natural world is full of tales of mysterious animal attacks on humans and inexplicable sightings of strange and sinister creatures. Wilderness experts Damian Duffy and Matt Hoffman decided to check out these stories for themselves and set off across the globe to investigate the reports. Using their experience and skills as a former army paratrooper (Damian) and an accomplished wildife photographer (Matt) they journey deep into the wild places and risk their lives to uncover the truth.Their investigations take them from the baffling and gory deaths of ranchers in Brazil to the return of a mythical Australian killer to the disappearance of villagers and farm animals in the Philippines and mystifying Alaskan sea creatures.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220210000 +0000" stop="20241220220000 +0000" channel="AnimalPlanet.lv"><title lang="lv">Edge of Alaska</title><desc lang="lv">McCarthy, Alaska is home to a rugged bunch of mavericks and risk takers, willing to brave the brutal conditions in this icy, isolated town. Once a thriving, prosperous place due to the gold rush, the town is now home to a mere 40 people. There is a juxtaposition between residents; while some believe in a traditional way of life, others are desperate to drag McCarthy into the modern age, believing this is the only way to ensure its survival. Edge of Alaska tells the story of this community at a crossroads.</desc></programme>
