<programme start="20241220073000 +0000" stop="20241220074500 +0000" channel="BalticumTV.lt"><title lang="lt">Everything is Told</title><desc lang="lt">Join our rotating cast of presenters, including Dominyk, Irma, and Timūras, as they host this weekday news and current affairs show, keeping us up to date with all of the major events occurring nationally in Lithuania and around the planet. With a focus on regional affairs, we are kept informed about developments on the border with Belarus, the Nord Stream 2 pipeline, the car pollution tax, Covid-19, and much more.</desc></programme>
