<programme start="20241220110000 +0000" stop="20241220120500 +0000" channel="BalticumTV.lt"><title lang="lt">Hold On There With Andrius Tapinas</title><desc lang="lt">This satirical comedic talk-show from Lithuania, hosted by Andrius Tapinas, explores everyday issues and provides insightful analysis of problems which affect the population. Each episode presents the views and opinions of guest journalists, public figures and comedians and is filmed before a live audience in different clubs in various cities across the country. The show pulls no punches as it provides what can be described as a more transparent, honest, and irreverent look at politics. It tries to hold those in positions of power to account and make them responsible for their actions and so it will appeal to open-minded viewers.</desc></programme>
