<programme start="20241220044000 +0000" stop="20241220050000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">The Amazing World of Gumball</title><desc lang="ee">Sarah the new kid in school is Gumball and Darwin&apos;s number one slightly obsessive fan. / The new coach at Elmore High stands up to Jamie. / The secret behind Anton&apos;s immortality. / The kids finally get the puppy they always wanted except it&apos;s a turtle. / When Mum reveals that Gumball&apos;s real name is Zach Gumball adopts a cheesy annoying persona to match the name. / Nothing much is happening for Gumball and Darwin and the background characters in Elmore seize their moment. / Gumball is in such a bad mood that it spreads to Darwin who joins him in complaining about everything. / The Wattersons are swapping scary stories on a family vacation when their car breaks down in the middle of the desert.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220051000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Bakugan</title><desc lang="ee">Strange occurrences begin to happen in and around Los Volmos, ELEMENTAL ENERGY from Vestroia is seeping into Earth creating strange phenomena and, causing Bakugan to rage out with excess energy. It&apos;s not all bad though, Vestroian Elemental Energy is also seeping into Bakugan causing ELEMENTAL EVOLUTIONS! Along with these new Evolutions comes a new breed of ELEMENTAL BRAWLERS - led by the brilliant biologist MARLOWE FAUSTUS and his super powerful Bakugan WRATH. Faustus established an academy to train the best and brightest Baku-Brawlers in the ways of Elemental Brawling, so they can protect the Earth from the increasingly dangerous eruptions of elemental energy. At the academy, the Awesome Brawlers learn to take Bakugan brawling to a new level unlocking a whole new set of awesome power sand evolutions! Even with these newly acquired powers, putting an end to the elemental storms and finding out who is responsible, is going to be to a challenge like no other.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220051000 +0000" stop="20241220053000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Bakugan</title><desc lang="ee">Strange occurrences begin to happen in and around Los Volmos, ELEMENTAL ENERGY from Vestroia is seeping into Earth creating strange phenomena and, causing Bakugan to rage out with excess energy. It&apos;s not all bad though, Vestroian Elemental Energy is also seeping into Bakugan causing ELEMENTAL EVOLUTIONS! Along with these new Evolutions comes a new breed of ELEMENTAL BRAWLERS - led by the brilliant biologist MARLOWE FAUSTUS and his super powerful Bakugan WRATH. Faustus established an academy to train the best and brightest Baku-Brawlers in the ways of Elemental Brawling, so they can protect the Earth from the increasingly dangerous eruptions of elemental energy. At the academy, the Awesome Brawlers learn to take Bakugan brawling to a new level unlocking a whole new set of awesome power sand evolutions! Even with these newly acquired powers, putting an end to the elemental storms and finding out who is responsible, is going to be to a challenge like no other.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220053000 +0000" stop="20241220053500 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">The Amazing World of Gumball</title><desc lang="ee">The Wattersons are a totally normal family. Dad is your regular 6&quot;4 pink rabbit who stays at home while Mom works in a rainbow factory. Their kids are pretty standard too - there&apos;s Gumball, a blue cat with a giant head, Anais, a 4 year old genius bunny, and Darwin, a pet goldfish that became part of the family when he sprouted legs. At the heart of the show is Gumball, who faces the trials and tribulations of any twelve-year-old kid - like being chased by a rampaging T-Rex, sleeping rough when a robot steals his identity, or dressing as a cheerleader and doing the splits to impress the girl of his dreams. Simple everyday issues we&apos;ve all been through. Gumball&apos;s hometown of Elmore is every bit as commonplace… a cactus waters his front lawn, a furry slug drives to work, and on the corner a balloon, a potato and a ghost all wait for the school bus. Welcome to The Amazing World of Gumball, where normal just got a little bit weird…</desc></programme>
