<programme start="20241220101000 +0000" stop="20241220102000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">The Amazing World of Gumball</title><desc lang="lv">Mom has forced Dad to install a password on the computer. The pop-up clue advises them that the password is the name of Dad&apos;s favorite child. After trying &quot;Gumball&quot; and &quot;Darwin&quot; unsuccessfully, they discover the answer is, in fact, &quot;Anais&quot;. They are determined to become Dad&apos;s favourites by any means necessary, even if it means undermining each other, plotting against Anais or driving a wedge between mom and dad.</desc></programme>
