<programme start="20241220154000 +0000" stop="20241220155000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Craig of the Creek</title><desc lang="lv">Craig and his two best friends, Kelsey and JP, are always going on adventures in the untamed suburban wilderness known as the Creek - a kid utopia where tribes of children rule over tree forts and bike ramps, making up an entire kid society. Each episode finds the kids either venturing into unexplored areas of the Creek, encountering new Creek Kids, or just getting into trouble at their hang out - the Stump.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220155000 +0000" stop="20241220160000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Craig of the Creek</title><desc lang="lv">Animated comedy following the adventures of Craig and his two friends Kelsey and JP. In this musical episode, Craig is suffering from the indoor blues as it continues to rain, preventing him and his friends from going to the Creek. At his father&apos;s suggestion, Craig decides to invent an imaginary adventure for him and his friends where they find a mysterious key at the Creek and try to discover what it could lead to.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220160000 +0000" stop="20241220161000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Craig of the Creek</title><desc lang="lv">&lt;I&gt; The Ground Is Lava!&lt;/I&gt; Animated comedy following the adventures of Craig and his two friends Kelsey and JP as they explore the wilderness of the creek together. When Craig berates Jessica for her lack of &apos;character design&apos;, Toman suddenly calls out for a game of The Ground Is Lava, forcing all the kids to rush to grounded objects for protection. Realising that he left Jessica all alone at the Creek, the Stump Kids make a trek to reach her before the dinner horn... or before Jessica becomes a victim of the game.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220161000 +0000" stop="20241220163000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Craig of the Creek</title><desc lang="lv">Animated comedy following the adventures of Craig and his two friends Kelsey and JP as they explore the wilderness of the creek together. In a parody of the Marvel Cinematic Universe, bees have suddenly taken over the Trading Tree - after getting stung, Craig is forced to reform the Council of the Creek once again. Things seem to be running smoothly when transferring the colony - that is, until council member Bobby suddenly steals the bees for himself in an effort to procure honey from them.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220163000 +0000" stop="20241220164000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">The Amazing World of Gumball</title><desc lang="lv">Gumball experiences an impossibly unfortunate chain of events. / When they find Anais training herself for a brutal showdown Gumball and Darwin realise that their sister is being pestered at school by an annoying kid: Billy. / An impromptu hug with a stranger at school leaves Gumball in an increasingly awkward social situation. / Mom and the kids depart for their hard day&apos;s work leaving a seemingly lazy Dad half-asleep on the sofa. Mom has given him one very simple job: buy mayonnaise. / The Watterson family&apos;s search for a parking space at the mall takes a little longer than expected. / Gumball and Darwin persuade Bobert to upgrade his operating system, then start to wish they hadn&apos;t. / Gumball is the star of his own comic, but struggles to match up to his heroic alter-ego. / Gumball tries to recapture the magic with Penny by organising a big romantic gesture. / Gumball and Darwin try to tear themselves away from the internet, but end up falling down the Elmore Stream-hole. 1</desc></programme>
