<programme start="20241220195500 +0000" stop="20241220200500 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Bakugan</title><desc lang="lv">Strange occurrences begin to happen in and around Los Volmos, ELEMENTAL ENERGY from Vestroia is seeping into Earth creating strange phenomena and, causing Bakugan to rage out with excess energy. It&apos;s not all bad though, Vestroian Elemental Energy is also seeping into Bakugan causing ELEMENTAL EVOLUTIONS! Along with these new Evolutions comes a new breed of ELEMENTAL BRAWLERS - led by the brilliant biologist MARLOWE FAUSTUS and his super powerful Bakugan WRATH. Faustus established an academy to train the best and brightest Baku-Brawlers in the ways of Elemental Brawling, so they can protect the Earth from the increasingly dangerous eruptions of elemental energy. At the academy, the Awesome Brawlers learn to take Bakugan brawling to a new level unlocking a whole new set of awesome power sand evolutions! Even with these newly acquired powers, putting an end to the elemental storms and finding out who is responsible, is going to be to a challenge like no other.</desc></programme>
