<programme start="20241221040000 +0000" stop="20241221041500 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">The Amazing World of Gumball</title><desc lang="lv">The Wattersons are a totally normal family. Dad is your regular 6&quot;4 pink rabbit who stays at home while Mom works in a rainbow factory. Their kids are pretty standard too - there&apos;s Gumball, a blue cat with a giant head, Anais, a 4 year old genius bunny, and Darwin, a pet goldfish that became part of the family when he sprouted legs. At the heart of the show is Gumball, who faces the trials and tribulations of any twelve-year-old kid - like being chased by a rampaging T-Rex, sleeping rough when a robot steals his identity, or dressing as a cheerleader and doing the splits to impress the girl of his dreams. Simple everyday issues we&apos;ve all been through. Gumball&apos;s hometown of Elmore is every bit as commonplace… a cactus waters his front lawn, a furry slug drives to work, and on the corner a balloon, a potato and a ghost all wait for the school bus. Welcome to The Amazing World of Gumball, where normal just got a little bit weird…</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221041500 +0000" stop="20241221043000 +0000" channel="CartoonNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">The Amazing World of Gumball</title><desc lang="lv">The Wattersons are swapping scary stories on a family vacation, when their car breaks down in the middle of the desert. They are left with no alternative but to trust a complete stranger, whose appearance matches the scary guy in Mom&apos;s story. When the stranger brings them to a derelict gas station, just as he did in mom&apos;s made-up scary story, the Wattersons can no longer pretend the story isn&apos;t coming true.</desc></programme>
