<programme start="20241220210000 +0000" stop="20241220220000 +0000" channel="CNNInternational.us"><title lang="en">Quest Means Business</title><desc lang="en">He&apos;s not messing around: Richard Quest presents his hot takes on the biggest breaking stories in the world of business. Watch for the expert analysis, commentary and opinions on the important headlines in the field from the notorious English journalist and CNN anchor. Joined by a cast of experts and correspondents delivering unrivaled facts and news, but also features and fascinating takes, figures and analysis on everything going down in the world of business.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220220000 +0000" stop="20241220223000 +0000" channel="CNNInternational.us"><title lang="en">The Lead with Jake Tapper</title><desc lang="en">News, politics and current affairs programme hosted by the award-winning, American journalist and author, Jake Tapper. Jake Tapper is the chief Washington correspondent for CNN and he will share his knowledge and insight into politics as well as covering a variety of other topics. This programme discusses a range of stories from topical events including national news, economics/finance, sports, health, technology and world affairs. The Lead with Jake Tapper has won a number of awards and accolades including three National Headliner Awards. Outside his work on television, Tapper has written for The New Yorker, The Washington Post and the Los Angeles Times as well as publishing his first novel, a political thriller.</desc></programme>
