<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220073000 +0000" channel="DiscoveryChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">How It&apos;s Made</title><desc lang="ee">Have you ever wondered how things that surround us every day are produced? Find out about the whole process from the beginning to the end in a documentary television series How It&apos;s Made. The series demonstrates how various items like clothing and accessories, food, industrial products, cars, musical instruments and many more are manufactured. Who would have thought how exciting it would be to watch a cupcake, formula 1 race car or gummy vitamins being made?</desc></programme>
