<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220193000 +0000" channel="DiscoveryChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Border Control: Spain</title><desc lang="ee">Going through customs can be a stressful experience for most people, even more so if you&apos;re attempting to smuggle drugs or weapons into the country. Follow the efforts of the Security and Customs Services at the border of Spain, as they work hard to keep their country safe from criminals. Whether it&apos;s drugs, weapons or even terrorism, there&apos;s a lot of things security have to consider in order to make sure all threats are handled properly. These security forces are always hot on the trail of suspicious activity, in the air, on land or away at sea.</desc></programme>
