<programme start="20241221034500 +0000" stop="20241221043000 +0000" channel="DocuBox.lv"><title lang="lv">Rip Files</title><desc lang="lv">The R.I.P. Files features a group of paranormal investigators, who use intuitive abilities and a deep knowledge of metaphysical techniques to interact with the entities they encounter at haunted locations. They encourage the spirits to share their stories in their own words through amazing EVPs and other evidence that is bridging the gap between the worlds of science and spirituality.</desc></programme>
