<programme start="20241220044000 +0000" stop="20241220054000 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">Monk</title><desc lang="ee">American comedy-drama detective mystery television series. Adrian Monk used to be a brilliant detective until his wife&apos;s death. Adrian believes her death is connected to her journalistic investigation but he can&apos;t find the killer. Loss of his beloved wife causes serious mental issues, numerous phobias and obsessive compulsive disorder. Thanks to his assistant, Sharona Fleming Adrian manages to break through and becomes a private detective and a consultant for the homicide unit.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220054000 +0000" stop="20241220063500 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">Hawaii Five-0</title><desc lang="ee">Contemporary reboot of the classic US crime series from 1868, focusing on a specialized police task force – Five-0 – led by former Navy SEAL Lt. Commander Steve McGarrett. Together with his chosen team of former New Jersey detective Danny Williams, a veteran Honolulu detective Chin Ho Kelly and his cousin, a rookie cop Kono Kalakaua, they pursue all manner of criminals in order to keep Hawaii safe.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220063500 +0000" stop="20241220073500 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">Chicago P.D.</title><desc lang="ee">The series follows the patrol officers and the Intelligence Unit of the 21st District of the Chicago Police Department as they pursue the pursue criminals. Every day they have to fight for safety in their beloved city and risk their lives. Detective Sergeant Henry Voight is the enigmatic and tough chief of the Chicago P.D.&apos;s Intelligence Unit. He is very loyal to the cops and detectives serving under him and has no limits on how far he will go to get criminals off the streets.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220073500 +0000" stop="20241220083000 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">Hudson &amp; Rex</title><desc lang="ee">A cop show with a difference as divorced Detective Charlie Hudson is teamed up with his new partner Rex, a highly trained law enforcement German Shepherd who was scheduled to be put to sleep after his former partner died. This action packed police procedural drama is set in the fictional St. John&apos;s Police Department and focuses on the partnership of man and dog and how they solve puzzling crimes using Charlie&apos;s skilled detective work and Rex&apos;s exceptional canine senses of smell and hearing. The pair are aided in their endeavours by Superintendent Donovan, Forensics Chief Truong, and IT Specialist Mills. Most of the episodes centre around different murders, each with their own unique twist.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220083000 +0000" stop="20241220092500 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">NCIS</title><desc lang="ee">Special Agent Leroy Jethro Gibbs is the leader of a team of special agents belonging to the NCIS (Naval Criminal Investigative Service) Major Case Response Team. Gibbs, a former Marine, is a tough investigator and a highly skilled interrogator who relies on his gut instinct as much as evidence. Gibbs&apos; second in command is Senior Field Agent Tony DiNozzo, a womanizing, movie-quoting former Baltimore Homicide Detective, who despite being the class clown always gets the job done. The team also consists of probationary field agent Ziva David, a former Mossad officer who is a skilled fighter, as well as Junior Field Agent Timothy McGee, a computer-savvy agent often mocked by DiNozzo. Assisting them are Abby Sciuto, the energetic-but-Goth lab tech who is like a daughter to Gibbs, and Dr. Donald Mallard, nicknamed Ducky, the eccentric medical examiner full of unusual stories.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220092500 +0000" stop="20241220102500 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">CSI: Vegas</title><desc lang="ee">Gil Grissom and Sara Sidle assist a team of investigators at the Las Vegas crime lab as they use the latest in forensic techniques to catch criminals who threaten the city and its people on a daily basis should justice fail.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220102500 +0000" stop="20241220112000 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">Criminal Minds</title><desc lang="ee">Criminal Minds shows everyday life of an elite team of special agents who work in the FBI&apos;s Behavioral Analysis Unit. They are trained to analyse line of thinking of criminals and foretell their next step and so prevent evil from happening. These specialists come to the rescue when all forces of police are engaged but the criminal is not detected. The agents use their unbelievable psychological methods, make themselves think like a criminal, analyse their characters and personalities.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220112000 +0000" stop="20241220121500 +0000" channel="Duo3.ee"><title lang="ee">Monk</title><desc lang="ee">American comedy-drama detective mystery television series. Adrian Monk used to be a brilliant detective until his wife&apos;s death. Adrian believes her death is connected to her journalistic investigation but he can&apos;t find the killer. Loss of his beloved wife causes serious mental issues, numerous phobias and obsessive compulsive disorder. Thanks to his assistant, Sharona Fleming Adrian manages to break through and becomes a private detective and a consultant for the homicide unit.</desc></programme>
