<programme start="20241220170000 +0000" stop="20241220180000 +0000" channel="Duo3.lv"><title lang="lv">Chicago P.D.</title><desc lang="lv">Jackie is back, but Zoey has mixed feelings about her return. Jackie bonds with an emotionally unstable, but charming, patient Vigilante Jones who claims to be a superhero. Dr. Prince inadvertently puts a patients life at risk, forcing Jackie to perform an important procedure on her own. Alarmed by his behavior, Jackie goes to Akalitus. Meanwhile, Zoey is shocked by Carries secret. Eddies in hot water at his job which could jeopardize Jackies position at All Saints.</desc></programme>
