<programme start="20241220044500 +0000" stop="20241220051000 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">Brooklyn Nine-Nine</title><desc lang="ee">Jake Peralta is Brooklyn&apos;s 99th precinct&apos;s best detective. The only mystery he hasn&apos;t solved, is how to grow up. When captain Holt is assigned as the precinct&apos;s new captain, Jake greets him with resistance, but after learning the challenges Holt has faced to get where he is today, the two begin to bond. Along with Amy Santiago, Rosa Diaz, Charles Boyle, Terry Jeffords, and the rest of the precinct, Jake solves crimes of the city, pursues criminal masterminds like the Pontiac bandit and tackles the hurdles of life in New York.</desc></programme>
