<programme start="20241220111500 +0000" stop="20241220114500 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">Married ... with Children</title><desc lang="ee">American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O&apos;Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he&apos;s not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220114500 +0000" stop="20241220121500 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">Married ... with Children</title><desc lang="ee">American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O&apos;Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he&apos;s not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220121500 +0000" stop="20241220124000 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">Young Sheldon</title><desc lang="ee">After giving an interview about the Superconducting Super Collider and how it could create a black hole and destroy the world, Dr. Sturgis gets fired, returns to town, and starts working at the grocery store, because he doesn&apos;t want his old job back. The Cooper family invites him over for dinner, and they all start talking about black holes and alternate universes. In one of the alternate universes, Dr. Sturgis is a cowboy, Connie is a New Yorker, George is a pastor, Mary is a seductress, Georgie is bald, Melissa is the genius and Sheldon is a normal kid.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220124000 +0000" stop="20241220130500 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">Young Sheldon</title><desc lang="ee">For 11-year-old Sheldon Cooper, it isn&apos;t easy growing up in East Texas. Being a once-in-a-generation mind capable of advanced mathematics and science isn&apos;t always helpful in a land where church and football are king. And while the vulnerable, gifted and somewhat naïve Sheldon deals with the world, his very normal family must find a way to deal with him. His father, George, is struggling to find his way as a high school football coach and as father to a boy he doesn&apos;t understand. Sheldon&apos;s mother, Mary, fiercely protects and nurtures her son in a town where he just doesn&apos;t fit in. Sheldon&apos;s older brother, Georgie, does the best he can in high school, but it&apos;s tough to be cool when you&apos;re in the same classes with your odd 11-year-old brother. Finally, there&apos;s Sheldon&apos;s twin sister, Missy, who sometimes resents all the attention Sheldon gets, but also remains the one person who can reliably tell Sheldon the truth.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220130500 +0000" stop="20241220133500 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">30 Rock</title><desc lang="ee">While the entire cast and crew is obsessed with watching the season finale of MILF Island, Liz tries to keep Jack from knowing that she is the person who made negative comments about him to a newspaper journalist.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220133500 +0000" stop="20241220140500 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">30 Rock</title><desc lang="ee">Jack asks Liz to get her ex-boyfriend Dennis for the show after he becomes a hero for saving someone at a subway station, and tries to get Tracy to become an African-American spokesman for the Republican party.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220140500 +0000" stop="20241220143500 +0000" channel="Duo6.ee"><title lang="ee">Brooklyn Nine-Nine</title><desc lang="ee">Jake Peralta is Brooklyn&apos;s 99th precinct&apos;s best detective. The only mystery he hasn&apos;t solved, is how to grow up. When captain Holt is assigned as the precinct&apos;s new captain, Jake greets him with resistance, but after learning the challenges Holt has faced to get where he is today, the two begin to bond. Along with Amy Santiago, Rosa Diaz, Charles Boyle, Terry Jeffords, and the rest of the precinct, Jake solves crimes of the city, pursues criminal masterminds like the Pontiac bandit and tackles the hurdles of life in New York.</desc></programme>
