<programme start="20241220200500 +0000" stop="20241220203000 +0000" channel="Duo6.lt"><title lang="lt">Married ... with Children</title><desc lang="lt">American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O&apos;Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he&apos;s not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.</desc></programme>
