<programme start="20241220214000 +0000" stop="20241220220500 +0000" channel="Duo6.lt"><title lang="lt">Two and a Half Men</title><desc lang="lt">After his divorce, Alan Harper, a struggling chiropractor, moves in with his brother Charlie Harper, a womanizer and successful jingle writer as Charlie &quot;temporarily&quot; allows him and his son Jake, a food-obsessed, lazy kid to join him in his luxurious beach-house complicating Charlie&apos;s carefree life. Compulsively neat and control-freak Alan, hedonistic free spirited bachelor Charlie, Jake and other peculiar characters - Evelyn, their vain mother, Charlie&apos;s outspoken cleaning lady Berta and his rich, self-confessed stalker neighbor Rose soon get themselves into an abundance of crazy and hilarious situations.</desc></programme>
