<programme start="20241220160000 +0000" stop="20241220163000 +0000" channel="Duo6.lv"><title lang="lv">Married ... with Children</title><desc lang="lv">American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O&apos;Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he&apos;s not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220163000 +0000" stop="20241220170000 +0000" channel="Duo6.lv"><title lang="lv">Married ... with Children</title><desc lang="lv">American comedy series. Al Bundy (Ed O&apos;Neill) was once a promising young high school American football player. Now he is a middle-aged and cynical shoe salesman living in the suburbs of Chicago. After a long day working in his unfulfilling job, he goes home to a family who irritate and disrespect him. His wife Peggy (Katey Sagal) is a lazy woman who spends the families money on herself and openly mocks and taunts Al. Their two children are Kelly and Bud. Kelly, the eldest daughter is not a bright kid. She dates a string of guys much to the annoyance of her father. Her younger brother Bud is a smart boy, but he&apos;s not what he would like to be - a hit with the ladies. Starring Christina Applegate as Kelly and David Faustino as Bud.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220170000 +0000" stop="20241220173000 +0000" channel="Duo6.lv"><title lang="lv">Friends</title><desc lang="lv">Delve into the hearts and minds of six friends living in New York City as they explore the anxieties and absurdities of true adulthood. This smart, sophisticated series offers a hilarious take on dating and working in the big city. As Rachel, Monica, Phoebe, Joey, Chandler and Ross realize, the search for happiness often seems to turn up more questions than answers. But while they look within for fulfillment, they also look out for one another during this exciting time when everything seems possible – as long as they&apos;ve got Friends.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220173000 +0000" stop="20241220180000 +0000" channel="Duo6.lv"><title lang="lv">Friends</title><desc lang="lv">Delve into the hearts and minds of six friends living in New York City as they explore the anxieties and absurdities of true adulthood. This smart, sophisticated series offers a hilarious take on dating and working in the big city. As Rachel, Monica, Phoebe, Joey, Chandler and Ross realize, the search for happiness often seems to turn up more questions than answers. But while they look within for fulfillment, they also look out for one another during this exciting time when everything seems possible – as long as they&apos;ve got Friends.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220180000 +0000" stop="20241220182500 +0000" channel="Duo6.lv"><title lang="lv">Brooklyn Nine-Nine</title><desc lang="lv">Jake Peralta is Brooklyn&apos;s 99th precinct&apos;s best detective. The only mystery he hasn&apos;t solved, is how to grow up. When captain Holt is assigned as the precinct&apos;s new captain, Jake greets him with resistance, but after learning the challenges Holt has faced to get where he is today, the two begin to bond. Along with Amy Santiago, Rosa Diaz, Charles Boyle, Terry Jeffords, and the rest of the precinct, Jake solves crimes of the city, pursues criminal masterminds like the Pontiac bandit and tackles the hurdles of life in New York.</desc></programme>
