<programme start="20241220185500 +0000" stop="20241220192000 +0000" channel="Duo6.lv"><title lang="lv">The Big Bang Theory</title><desc lang="lv">Meet four brilliant but socially awkward scientists- Leonard Hofstadter, an experimental physicist with an IQ of 173, Sheldon Cooper, a theoretical physicist researching quantum mechanics and string theory, who are roommates, colleagues and best friends, and their friends Howard Wolowitz, an aerospace engineer and Rajesh Koothrappali, a particle astrophysicist. When they are not working, boys are hanging out together, playing video games, watching science-fiction movies or reading comic books. Their lives will change forever when a pretty woman and an aspiring actress named Penny moves into an apartment across the hall from Leonard and Sheldon showing them there is more to life outside the laboratory.</desc></programme>
