<programme start="20241220165500 +0000" stop="20241220171000 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Uue aja asjad</title><desc lang="ee">Arhiivimaterjalidele tuginev sari, mis esitab tegelikkust ajavahemikus 1985-2005. Saade &quot;Söök ja jook&quot; jutustab sellest, kuidas toit poest otsa sai ja eestlased olid sunnitud paljuräägitud kartulikooredieedile jääma. Siis ajad muutusid. Toitu sai palju ja see oli nii maitsev, et tuli jääda järgmisele dieedile - sedakord kaalu langetama. Teksti autor Juku-Kalle Raid, teksti loeb Juhan Ulfsak. Režissöör Anne Mäns, produtsent Olavi Paide. Tootja Ruut.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220171000 +0000" stop="20241220173500 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Üksildane Uitaja ja Don Quijote Tallinnas</title><desc lang="ee">Pisikene jalutuskäik Tallinna vanalinna. Suurepärane olustikupilt taasiseseisvunud Eesti räämas ja peremeest otsivast pealinnast. 90ndate aastateÜksildase Uitajana kõnnib Lauri Leesi ja Don Quijotena Tiina Mägi.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220173500 +0000" stop="20241220183500 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Pilvede all</title><desc lang="ee">Kodumaine draamasari suhetest, saladustest ja romantikast. Täiskasvanuks saades ja kodust lahkudes kaotasid kolm õde (Elisabet Tamm, Liis Haab ja Inga Allik) üksteist silmist, igaühel oli oma elu ja omad unistused. Nüüd, aastaid hiljem, toob nende ema tabav õnnetus õed taas kokku ja lisaks tänastele probleemidele hakkavad pinnale kerkima ka seni kiivalt varjatud minevikusündmused.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220183500 +0000" stop="20241220191000 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Naerda või mitte naerda…</title><desc lang="ee">Saates ütleb Heinz Valk ühe teise mehe sõnadega, et naer on üks inimsuse säilitamise võimalusi. Äkki ongi! Valdeko Vende lappab vanu ajalehti ja näitab esimesi naljapilte eesti ajakirjanduses. Saatejuht Moidela Tõnisson, režissöör Vilja Palm.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220191000 +0000" stop="20241220194000 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Klaver põõsas</title><desc lang="ee">Meelelahutuslik muusikasaade; stuudios olev žürii hindab nelja pala, millest üks on üllatuslaul; saatejuht Marko Reikop.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220194000 +0000" stop="20241220203000 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Mamma Mia</title><desc lang="ee">Populaarses naiste talk-shows jõuavad ekraanile lood elust enesest. Saadet juhib julge ja otsekohene Tuuli Roosma, kes valiti ka telehooaja parimaks nais-saatejuhiks.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220203000 +0000" stop="20241220220500 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Braavo</title><desc lang="ee">Meelelahutusšõu &quot;Braavo!&quot; läheb eetrisse Eesti suurimast, Volta kompleksi rajatud telestuudiost. Saadet juhivad Koit Toome ja Helen Sürje.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220220500 +0000" stop="20241221040000 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Elmar TV</title><desc lang="ee">Raadiost Elmar tuttav Eesti muusika kullafond ja ka värsked kodumaised hitid hoiavad Eesti Kanalis öösiti tuju üleval. Nostalgitse või laula kaasa, kodumaiste muusikavideote paremik on eetris!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221040000 +0000" stop="20241221040200 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Eesti Vabariigi hümn</title><desc lang="ee">Eesti Vabariigi hümn.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221040200 +0000" stop="20241221045500 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Kelgukoerad</title><desc lang="ee">Telesari kriminaaluurijatest, kel tuleb lahendada kõige keerulisemad juhtumid ja tabada ohlikud kurjategijad.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221045500 +0000" stop="20241221055000 +0000" channel="EestiKanal.ee"><title lang="ee">Kelgukoerad</title><desc lang="ee">Telesari kriminaaluurijatest, kel tuleb lahendada kõige keerulisemad juhtumid ja tabada ohlikud kurjategijad.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220041500 +0000" stop="20241220051500 +0000" channel="EpicDrama.ee"><title lang="ee">Murdoch Mysteries</title><desc lang="ee">Murdoch Mysteries is a fine example of canadian detective series. The main character is William Murdoch, a talented police detective working in Toronto, Ontario in the late 19th century. He uses methods of forensic science to solve the mysterious murder cases and these methods are ahead of his time. His motto is &quot;Nothing is impossible&quot; and his confidence and determination help him to cope with the most complicated tasks that are beyond the scope of other detectives. William is not alone in his investigations, his superior, inspector Brackenreid, Doctor Julia Ogden, expert skilled in pathology and the inexperienced but enthusiastic assistant Constable George Crabtree are by his side. Sometimes real historical figures appear in the series, such as Jack London, William Churchill, Nikola Tesla etc.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220051500 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="EpicDrama.ee"><title lang="ee">Grantchester</title><desc lang="ee">Drama series adapted from the novels by James Runcie about a village in Cambridgeshire where Sidney Chambers is the local vicar. When Guy and Amanda ask Sidney to perform their wedding ceremony, the heartbroken vicar takes solace in a bottle. In spite of his disappointment, Sidney helps Isabel Livingstone to prepare for her wedding to Arthur Evans despite her mother&apos;s wishes. However, when her mother Daisy is found dead, Sidney finds himself being dragged into the investigation reluctantly.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220065000 +0000" channel="EpicDrama.ee"><title lang="ee">Miss Scarlet and the Duke</title><desc lang="ee">Period crime series following Eliza Scarlet as she helps Scotland Yard solve various crimes and cases. After her father&apos;s sudden death, Eliza is left with no choice but to take on his detective business or face the prospect of poverty. She employs the rogue investigator William &apos;The Duke&apos; Wellington as her partner, as this is Victorian England, and she can&apos;t operate alone in a male dominated society. The duo embark on a crime solving relationship, often clashing due to their differing morals and opinions. Full of drama, the series stars Kate Phillips, Stuart Martin, Cathy Belton, Andrew Gower, Ansu Kabia and Kevin Doyle.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220065000 +0000" stop="20241220073500 +0000" channel="EpicDrama.ee"><title lang="ee">Murdoch Mysteries</title><desc lang="ee">Murdoch Mysteries is a fine example of canadian detective series. The main character is William Murdoch, a talented police detective working in Toronto, Ontario in the late 19th century. He uses methods of forensic science to solve the mysterious murder cases and these methods are ahead of his time. His motto is &quot;Nothing is impossible&quot; and his confidence and determination help him to cope with the most complicated tasks that are beyond the scope of other detectives. William is not alone in his investigations, his superior, inspector Brackenreid, Doctor Julia Ogden, expert skilled in pathology and the inexperienced but enthusiastic assistant Constable George Crabtree are by his side. Sometimes real historical figures appear in the series, such as Jack London, William Churchill, Nikola Tesla etc.</desc></programme>
