<programme start="20241220053000 +0000" stop="20241220075000 +0000" channel="FilmZone.lv"><title lang="lv">Training Day</title><desc lang="lv">Winner of an Academy Award for Best Actor for Denzel Washington. This compelling and gritty look at police corruption was nominated for two Academy Awards, including Best Supporting Actor for Ethan Hawke. Ethan Hawke (&quot;Snow Falling on Cedars&quot;) stars as a rookie LAPD officer who is paired with veteran officer Denzel Washington (&quot;Remember the Titans&quot;, &quot;Fallen&quot;) for a one-day ride-along to prove his mettle to join the narcotics unit on the tough, inner-city beat of Los Angeles. He soon realizes that the line between right and wrong has been severely blurred and that his training may not be all that it appears! Also features some of music&apos;s hottest talent, including Dr. Dre, Snoop Dogg and Macy Gray.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220075000 +0000" stop="20241220094000 +0000" channel="FilmZone.lv"><title lang="lv">Extract</title><desc lang="lv">Jason Bateman, Kristen Wiig, Ben Affleck and Mila Kunis star in Mike Judge&apos;s workplace comedy. Joel Reynolds (Bateman) is the founder of a company that produces and bottles flavour extracts. His marital love life has flatlined, but he can&apos;t bring himself to cheat on his wife Suzie (Wiig), until his friend Dean (Affleck) convinces him to hire a gigolo to seduce her, thus freeing Joel to also play the field. This will prove to be a worse idea than it sounds. But that will be the least of his worries, as a horrific accident in the bottling plant, a grifting employee (Kunis), an aggressive lawyer (Gene Simmons) and striking workers bring his company to its knees...</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220094000 +0000" stop="20241220114500 +0000" channel="FilmZone.lv"><title lang="lv">Shotgun Wedding</title><desc lang="lv">Darcy and Tom gather their families for the ultimate destination wedding, but when the entire wedding party is taken hostage the bride and groom must save their loved ones--if they don&apos;t kill each other first.</desc></programme>
