<programme start="20241220041000 +0000" stop="20241220050000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Holiday Baking Championship</title><desc lang="ee">Eight bakers show off their skills in this Holiday-themed baking competition series with the winner taking home a whopping $50,000. With three expert judges analysing their baked treats, every mistake is identified, so these eight bakers must whip, cream, and ice to perfection if they hope to progress to the final rounds of the competition. The challenges are of course Holiday-themed, thus testing their creativity and ability to adapt. Each episode is comprised of two rounds, with the worst performing baker eliminated every week until only one remains.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220054500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Chopped Junior</title><desc lang="ee">Ted Allen hosts this hearty American cooking show that sees four little chefs showcasing their cooking abilities as they prepare and present delicious dishes for the chance to win a whopping $10,000 cash prize. This spin off version of popular cooking competition Chopped is like a breathe of fresh air as these young prodigies bring their youthful energy and originality to the Chopped kitchen. The delicious treats and competitive format is bound to leave you wanting more.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220054500 +0000" stop="20241220061000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Celebrate! With Chef Nti</title><desc lang="ee">Cooking - Ep. 7. Chef Nti marks special celebrations with something cooked from the heart. She prepares recipes that are easy and entertaining for every occasion.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220061000 +0000" stop="20241220065500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Best Baker in America</title><desc lang="ee">Cooking competition show in which professional and home bakers compete in a baking tournament. For six weeks, eight skilled bakers are challenged to use their style and technical abilities to make stunning, tasty treats and impress the judges - from macarons, fruit tarts, creme brulee to spectacular and elaborately-decorated cakes. One person gets eliminated every week by the panel of judges, until the final where the best three bakers compete for the grand prize of $25,000 and the title of &apos;&apos;Best Baker in America&apos;&apos;.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220065500 +0000" stop="20241220071700 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Bobby Flay&apos;s Barbecue Addiction</title><desc lang="ee">There&apos;s nothing more satisfying than taking to the open air, armed with a trusty barbecue, and grilling up some delicious cuts of meat. In this unique series, chef Bobby Flay does exactly that, bringing the viewer along with him as he demonstrates the art of a good barbecue, complete with expert grilling techniques. Using ingredients from around the world, and with an entertaining them each episode, Bobby puts the flames to the test, delivering the perfect barbecuing experience.</desc></programme>
