<programme start="20241220074000 +0000" stop="20241220080200 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives</title><desc lang="ee">Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives is American food reality television series about places with the most delicious food. The host is American restaurateur Guy Fieri who travels along the USA, Canada or Europe looking for the most fascinating cafes and introduces them to the viewers. Each show has a specific focus on a certain dish, like burgers, pasta, comfort food. Small cafes with traditional food and home-style recipes or ethnic specialties adored by the locals are of particular interest to the host. Guy Fieri enters the kitchen, gets to know the cook, actively takes part in cooking, interacts with the guests and kitchen staff and gives his humorous spicy comments on the process and the food itself.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220080200 +0000" stop="20241220082500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives</title><desc lang="ee">Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives is American food reality television series about places with the most delicious food. The host is American restaurateur Guy Fieri who travels along the USA, Canada or Europe looking for the most fascinating cafes and introduces them to the viewers. Each show has a specific focus on a certain dish, like burgers, pasta, comfort food. Small cafes with traditional food and home-style recipes or ethnic specialties adored by the locals are of particular interest to the host. Guy Fieri enters the kitchen, gets to know the cook, actively takes part in cooking, interacts with the guests and kitchen staff and gives his humorous spicy comments on the process and the food itself.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220082500 +0000" stop="20241220091000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Restaurant: Impossible</title><desc lang="ee">Owning and operating a restaurant is hard graft, harder than many believe it to be. Long hours, stiff competition, and no guarantees that customers will frequent; for many budding restaurateurs, the dream often turns into a nightmare. This American reality series follows English celebrity chef Robert Irvine as he attempts to save failing restaurants from the brink of collapse. With just two days to turn it around on a measly budget of $10,000, he gets to straight to work identifying and altering the businesses&apos; weaknesses before a grand re-opening. Can he achieve the seemingly impossible and create a food establish that is set to succeed?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220091000 +0000" stop="20241220095500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">The Kitchen</title><desc lang="ee">Join chefs Sunny Anderson, Jeff Mauro, Marcela Valladolid as well as chef Katie Lee and Iron Chef Geoffrey Zakarian as they show you how to make simple and delicious meals for your friends and family, while also having lots of fun together in &apos;&apos;The Kitchen&apos;&apos;. With interesting and easy recipes, incredible guests, and hilarious hosts and their amazing interaction, you will enjoy this cooking-themed talk show.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220095500 +0000" stop="20241220101700 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Girl Meets Farm</title><desc lang="ee">Molly Yeh is a cookbook author who combines her country lifestyle with her Jewish and Chinese heritage to create the most delicious new dishes. A former big city girl, Yeh is multi talented, a successful blogger and classically trained musician, its food that ultimately stole her heart. Learn lots of tricks and tips with Yeh as she cooks up her personal favourite recipes for every occasion, from family visits to brunch with the girls to a classic farm supper! This show is an absolute treat.</desc></programme>
