<programme start="20241220134000 +0000" stop="20241220140200 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">The Pioneer Woman</title><desc lang="ee">Ree Drummon is a writer, photographer, ranch wife and mother of four. She is the host of cooking show The Pioneer Woman. She cooks in a simple, easy to follow way at her ranch in Pawhuska, Oklahoma. We can learn new techniques and get new ideas in a down to earth way and feed even big families every day with dishes that are both yummy and healthy. It is surprisingly easy to cook following her recipes step by step. Her passion for cooking is appreciated by more than 22 million of people all over the world.</desc></programme>
