<programme start="20241220142500 +0000" stop="20241220144700 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Beat Bobby Flay</title><desc lang="ee">Beat Bobby Flay is an exciting American Cooking show in which two contestants create mouth watering dishes in competition with each other, for the chance to go head to head with the one and only Bobby Flay himself. Flay gets to pick one key ingredient that the contestants must use before the winner is decided by guests of the show. The winner of the first round must then beat Flay in a 45 minute round. The overall winner is then decided by a panel of celebrity judges. So the question is, who can beat the Flayster?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220144700 +0000" stop="20241220151000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Beat Bobby Flay</title><desc lang="ee">Beat Bobby Flay is an exciting American Cooking show in which two contestants create mouth watering dishes in competition with each other, for the chance to go head to head with the one and only Bobby Flay himself. Flay gets to pick one key ingredient that the contestants must use before the winner is decided by guests of the show. The winner of the first round must then beat Flay in a 45 minute round. The overall winner is then decided by a panel of celebrity judges. So the question is, who can beat the Flayster?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220151000 +0000" stop="20241220160000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Christmas Cookie Challenge</title><desc lang="ee">Reality competition for the festive period. A group of talented bakers hope to impress the judges with their Christmas cookies as they face a series of themed challenges. The judges will be looking for inventiveness, decorating skills and, of course, deliciously baked Christmas cookies. Whoever can wow the judges and blow away the competition will take home a huge cash prize.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220160000 +0000" stop="20241220174000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Holiday Baking Championship</title><desc lang="ee">Eight bakers show off their skills in this Holiday-themed baking competition series with the winner taking home a whopping $50,000. With three expert judges analysing their baked treats, every mistake is identified, so these eight bakers must whip, cream, and ice to perfection if they hope to progress to the final rounds of the competition. The challenges are of course Holiday-themed, thus testing their creativity and ability to adapt. Each episode is comprised of two rounds, with the worst performing baker eliminated every week until only one remains.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220174000 +0000" stop="20241220182500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Restaurant: Impossible</title><desc lang="ee">Owning and operating a restaurant is hard graft, harder than many believe it to be. Long hours, stiff competition, and no guarantees that customers will frequent; for many budding restaurateurs, the dream often turns into a nightmare. This American reality series follows English celebrity chef Robert Irvine as he attempts to save failing restaurants from the brink of collapse. With just two days to turn it around on a measly budget of $10,000, he gets to straight to work identifying and altering the businesses&apos; weaknesses before a grand re-opening. Can he achieve the seemingly impossible and create a food establish that is set to succeed?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220182500 +0000" stop="20241220191000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">The Kitchen</title><desc lang="ee">Join chefs Sunny Anderson, Jeff Mauro, Marcela Valladolid as well as chef Katie Lee and Iron Chef Geoffrey Zakarian as they show you how to make simple and delicious meals for your friends and family, while also having lots of fun together in &apos;&apos;The Kitchen&apos;&apos;. With interesting and easy recipes, incredible guests, and hilarious hosts and their amazing interaction, you will enjoy this cooking-themed talk show.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220191000 +0000" stop="20241220193200 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.ee"><title lang="ee">Girl Meets Farm</title><desc lang="ee">Molly Yeh is a cookbook author who combines her country lifestyle with her Jewish and Chinese heritage to create the most delicious new dishes. A former big city girl, Yeh is multi talented, a successful blogger and classically trained musician, its food that ultimately stole her heart. Learn lots of tricks and tips with Yeh as she cooks up her personal favourite recipes for every occasion, from family visits to brunch with the girls to a classic farm supper! This show is an absolute treat.</desc></programme>
