<programme start="20241220204000 +0000" stop="20241220212500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Holiday Baking Championship</title><desc lang="lv">Eight bakers show off their skills in this Holiday-themed baking competition series with the winner taking home a whopping $50,000. With three expert judges analysing their baked treats, every mistake is identified, so these eight bakers must whip, cream, and ice to perfection if they hope to progress to the final rounds of the competition. The challenges are of course Holiday-themed, thus testing their creativity and ability to adapt. Each episode is comprised of two rounds, with the worst performing baker eliminated every week until only one remains.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220212500 +0000" stop="20241220214700 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">The Pioneer Woman</title><desc lang="lv">Ree Drummon is a writer, photographer, ranch wife and mother of four. She is the host of cooking show The Pioneer Woman. She cooks in a simple, easy to follow way at her ranch in Pawhuska, Oklahoma. We can learn new techniques and get new ideas in a down to earth way and feed even big families every day with dishes that are both yummy and healthy. It is surprisingly easy to cook following her recipes step by step. Her passion for cooking is appreciated by more than 22 million of people all over the world.</desc></programme>
