<programme start="20241220221000 +0000" stop="20241220223200 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Beat Bobby Flay</title><desc lang="lv">Beat Bobby Flay is an exciting American Cooking show in which two contestants create mouth watering dishes in competition with each other, for the chance to go head to head with the one and only Bobby Flay himself. Flay gets to pick one key ingredient that the contestants must use before the winner is decided by guests of the show. The winner of the first round must then beat Flay in a 45 minute round. The overall winner is then decided by a panel of celebrity judges. So the question is, who can beat the Flayster?</desc></programme>
