<programme start="20241220225500 +0000" stop="20241220234000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Chopped</title><desc lang="lv">Chopped is an American reality cooking TV game show hosted by Ted Allen. Four chefs compete against each other. At the beginning of each round they receive a basket containing four mystery ingredients and are expected to create the best three-course meal using every single one of them. Each round has a time limit. The dishes are judged based on their presentation, taste and creativity. At the end of every round one chef is &quot;chopped&quot; from the competition with no prize. The winner can get up to $50.000.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220234000 +0000" stop="20241221002500 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Chopped Junior</title><desc lang="lv">Ted Allen hosts this hearty American cooking show that sees four little chefs showcasing their cooking abilities as they prepare and present delicious dishes for the chance to win a whopping $10,000 cash prize. This spin off version of popular cooking competition Chopped is like a breathe of fresh air as these young prodigies bring their youthful energy and originality to the Chopped kitchen. The delicious treats and competitive format is bound to leave you wanting more.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221002500 +0000" stop="20241221011000 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Best Baker in America</title><desc lang="lv">Cooking competition show in which professional and home bakers compete in a baking tournament. For six weeks, eight skilled bakers are challenged to use their style and technical abilities to make stunning, tasty treats and impress the judges - from macarons, fruit tarts, creme brulee to spectacular and elaborately-decorated cakes. One person gets eliminated every week by the panel of judges, until the final where the best three bakers compete for the grand prize of $25,000 and the title of &apos;&apos;Best Baker in America&apos;&apos;.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221011000 +0000" stop="20241221013200 +0000" channel="FoodNetwork.lv"><title lang="lv">Bobby Flay&apos;s Barbecue Addiction</title><desc lang="lv">There&apos;s nothing more satisfying than taking to the open air, armed with a trusty barbecue, and grilling up some delicious cuts of meat. In this unique series, chef Bobby Flay does exactly that, bringing the viewer along with him as he demonstrates the art of a good barbecue, complete with expert grilling techniques. Using ingredients from around the world, and with an entertaining them each episode, Bobby puts the flames to the test, delivering the perfect barbecuing experience.</desc></programme>
