<programme start="20241220045500 +0000" stop="20241220054500 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">The Walking Dead</title><desc lang="ee">American post-apocalyptic horror TV series follows survivors of a zombie apocalypse, trying to stay alive. Sheriff&apos;s deputy Rick Grimes awakens from a coma to find out that the world has drastically changed. He leads a group of survivors and together they struggle to pull through in the world overrun by zombies, that are attracted to noise and to different scents, especially the human scent. Humans bitten or scratched by them become infected and turn into zombies as well.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220054500 +0000" stop="20241220061000 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">Solar Opposites</title><desc lang="ee">Korvo and Terry place nanobots in the city&apos;s water supply to spy on their neighbors. Learning they are not well-liked, Korvo and Terry use the information from the nanobots to win over the community, and run for president of their homeowner association. The nanobots form a sentient person that runs for president as well, and all three expose embarrassing secrets about their neighbors, who break out in violence. The incumbent president Ruth restores order and turns the crowd against Korvo, Terry, and the nanobot person, who escapes from Korvo. Jesse - concerned that Yumyulack is shrinking and capturing too many humans - uses technology to manipulate people who were mean to Yumyulack, hoping to teach him that humans are generally kind.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220061000 +0000" stop="20241220064500 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">Solar Opposites</title><desc lang="ee">How would Earth look to alien settlers? Awesome or awful? Well that&apos;s the contrasting opinions of an alien family in this animated American sitcom. A year ago, the alien family fled the destruction of their planet Shlorp and crashed on Earth, beginning a new life in foreign surroundings, where they must adjust to the idiosyncrasies of the human world. The family is made up of partners Korvo and Terry, and their child-replicants Yumyulack and Jesse. The show was created by Justin Roiland (Rick and Morty) and Mike McMahan, with voices provided by Roiland, Thomas Middleditch, Sean Giambrone, and Mary Mack, among others.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220064500 +0000" stop="20241220074000 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">Criminal Minds</title><desc lang="ee">Criminal Minds shows everyday life of an elite team of special agents who work in the FBI&apos;s Behavioral Analysis Unit. They are trained to analyse line of thinking of criminals and foretell their next step and so prevent evil from happening. These specialists come to the rescue when all forces of police are engaged but the criminal is not detected. The agents use their unbelievable psychological methods, make themselves think like a criminal, analyse their characters and personalities.</desc></programme>
