<programme start="20241220083000 +0000" stop="20241220092500 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">9-1-1</title><desc lang="ee">The series follows the lives of Los Angeles first responders: police officers, paramedics, firefighters and dispatchers and their high-pressure experience. These heroic people work day and night to ensure safety and support to those in trouble. First responders have to work together as one strong unit, as various accidents can happen anytime anywhere and if they do not react, the consequences will be horrible. Every day in the city and around it extreme emergencies happen, requiring immediate response.</desc></programme>
