<programme start="20241220101500 +0000" stop="20241220110500 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">Bones</title><desc lang="ee">Adrenaline-filled dramedy series that follows the crime-solving adventures of a forensic anthropologist, Dr. Temperance &apos;&apos;Bones&apos;&apos; Brennan, and an FBI agent Seeley Booth. The unusual couple investigates various murder cases and discovers causes of death by examining human remains. Dr. Brennan and her team at the Jeffersonian Institute Medico-Legal Lab, provide scientific expertise and Special Agent Seeley Booth provides FBI criminal investigation technique for each case, and together, they are a match made in heaven when it comes to solving some strange and gripping mysteries and bringing culprits to justice.</desc></programme>
