<programme start="20241220232500 +0000" stop="20241221001000 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">This Is Us</title><desc lang="ee">Follow the extraordinary lives of parents Jack and Rebecca Pearson, and their three children known as the &apos;&apos;Big Three&apos;&apos; - Kevin, Kate and Randall, through several different time frames. Rebecca had a difficult pregnancy with triplets, and after they lost one child, the Pearsons decide to adopt Randall who was born the same day. As years go by, we have a chance to see their incredible journeys and struggles after Jack&apos;s death - Rebecca&apos;s new marriage, Randall&apos;s story as he becomes a successful finance professional and a father of three, Kevin&apos;s life as an actor while struggling to be taken seriously, and Kate&apos;s struggles with weight issues.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221001000 +0000" stop="20241221005000 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">Criminal Minds</title><desc lang="ee">Criminal Minds shows everyday life of an elite team of special agents who work in the FBI&apos;s Behavioral Analysis Unit. They are trained to analyse line of thinking of criminals and foretell their next step and so prevent evil from happening. These specialists come to the rescue when all forces of police are engaged but the criminal is not detected. The agents use their unbelievable psychological methods, make themselves think like a criminal, analyse their characters and personalities.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221005000 +0000" stop="20241221014500 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">War of the Worlds</title><desc lang="ee">H. G. Wells&apos; classic War of the Worlds is given a fresh look in this chilling re-telling set-in modern-day Europe that begins with French scientists receiving a signal confirming the existence of extra-terrestrials. The 8-episode TV mini-series follows a group of survivors facing the post-apocalyptic world left behind after an alien strike wipes out all but only a handful of the Earths&apos; population. The FOX developed series is an Anglo-French production starring Georgina Rich and Michael Marcus trying to find their way through their new existence in a world that bares similarities to &apos;Walking Dead&apos;.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221014500 +0000" stop="20241221023000 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">The Walking Dead</title><desc lang="ee">American post-apocalyptic horror TV series follows survivors of a zombie apocalypse, trying to stay alive. Sheriff&apos;s deputy Rick Grimes awakens from a coma to find out that the world has drastically changed. He leads a group of survivors and together they struggle to pull through in the world overrun by zombies, that are attracted to noise and to different scents, especially the human scent. Humans bitten or scratched by them become infected and turn into zombies as well.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221023000 +0000" stop="20241221031500 +0000" channel="FX.ee"><title lang="ee">The Walking Dead</title><desc lang="ee">American post-apocalyptic horror TV series follows survivors of a zombie apocalypse, trying to stay alive. Sheriff&apos;s deputy Rick Grimes awakens from a coma to find out that the world has drastically changed. He leads a group of survivors and together they struggle to pull through in the world overrun by zombies, that are attracted to noise and to different scents, especially the human scent. Humans bitten or scratched by them become infected and turn into zombies as well.</desc></programme>
