<programme start="20241220111000 +0000" stop="20241220131500 +0000" channel="Go3Sport1.ee"><title lang="ee">Football: Ligue 1. Monaco - Paris SG</title><desc lang="ee">PSG, AS Monaco, Marseille, Olympique Lyonnais &amp; Lille... just to name a few. Ligue 1 is currently full of well-organised football teams and incredible European talent, who are a complement to the sport. As the highest professional division in France, it has established itself as one of the top five leagues on the continent. Lyon are the most successful team in regards to consecutive titles, whereas PSG and AS Monaco have managed to propel themselves to the highest achievements in the league, with calculated foreign investment. With the latter coming from a principality, Ligue 1 is another example of a domestic league that provides cross-border competition. From southern wine-growing regions such as Bordeaux, to the historically renowned capital of Paris, we cover the whole of France.</desc></programme>
