<programme start="20241221020000 +0000" stop="20241221023000 +0000" channel="HGTV.ee"><title lang="ee">Beachfront Bargain Hunt</title><desc lang="ee">Attempting to bring families&apos; dreams come to life, but on a budget, Beachfront Bargain Hunt shows that you don&apos;t have to be a millionaire if you want to live a life by the sea! Narrated by John Beach, this show follows a number of couples, families and people looking just for themselves exploring various beachfront&apos;s in USA, looking for homes that won&apos;t break the bank. Ensuring each person gets what they want, they are introduced to a number of properties that meet their ultimate dream home in the hopes that they will indeed find the one. With 101 episodes, Beachfront Bargain Hunt introduces you to the life that can be led, without breaking to bank, to live a life by the sea!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221023000 +0000" stop="20241221030000 +0000" channel="HGTV.ee"><title lang="ee">House Hunters</title><desc lang="ee">American reality series following host Suzanne Whang on her quest to help people relocate in search of their dream home. Follow the individuals, couples and families in an international search for their perfect property, exploring a stunning selection of homes chosen just for them. With three potential candidates to choose from, join them as they try and make the difficult decision to start a new life abroad. Revisit the new homeowners at the end of each episode to see how their properties have developed and how life has changed for them since the move.</desc></programme>
