<programme start="20241220180000 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="HGTV.lv"><title lang="lv">Unsellable Houses</title><desc lang="lv">Real estate consultants and twin sisters Leslie Davis and Lyndsay Lamb have a knack for helping desperate homeowners sell their lifeless homes. After visiting nearby comparables, the sisters make the necessary, impactful renovations that convert these unlovable houses into diamonds in the rough.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220200000 +0000" channel="HGTV.lv"><title lang="lv">Celebrity IOU</title><desc lang="lv">Follow an array of Hollywood superstars as they embark on an exciting and heart-warming mission, expressing their gratitude to the most important people in their lives by surprising them with huge and incredible home renovations. There to help them on their adventure are twin brothers Drew and Jonathan Scott. Some of the amazing people featured on the programme are Rebel Wilson, Bred Pitt, Jeremy Renner, Michael Buble, Allison Janney, LeAnn Rimes, Kevin Hart, and many others.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220200000 +0000" stop="20241220210000 +0000" channel="HGTV.lv"><title lang="lv">Happy to be Home with the Benkos</title><desc lang="lv">Gray helps a growing family tiptoe into colour. Meanwhile, Grumpy makes the historical home more functional, adding much-needed storage.</desc></programme>
