<programme start="20241220220000 +0000" stop="20241220230000 +0000" channel="HGTV.lv"><title lang="lv">Divided By Design</title><desc lang="lv">A family live upstairs through a lengthy reno. After delays, the Coral Gables project moves forward. Ray and Eilyn assess reno on their forever home.</desc></programme>
