<programme start="20241221010000 +0000" stop="20241221013000 +0000" channel="HGTV.lv"><title lang="lv">My Lottery Dream Home</title><desc lang="lv">This is a property hunting show with a very expensive twist. David Bromstad joins people as they search for their dream homes with a dreamy budget, that&apos;s because all of the guest on this particular house hunting show are lottery winners. Whether these lucky families are after a family home in the suburbs outside Boston with a yard big enough for a swing set and pool, or a classy but understated home in quiet and relaxed Bethany Beach, Delaware, property expert Bromstad is sure to find the perfect pad.</desc></programme>
