<programme start="20241220113000 +0000" stop="20241220121500 +0000" channel="History.ee"><title lang="ee">The Curse of Oak Island</title><desc lang="ee">The Curse of Oak Island is an active reality television series that focuses on the Oak Island mystery. There are numerous mystical stories of buried treasure and unexplained objects on or near this enigmatic island in Nova Scotia. Since the 19th century several attempts have been taken to locate treasure and artifacts there, some people even lost their lives trying to read this riddle. The Lagina brothers, Rick and Marty, were so impressed by this legend that they decided to try their luck and start this dangerous mission with the help of modern technologies and machinery. They are hammering at finding whatever is there, hidden deep under the ground, taking no notice of the fact that so far not even one research has ended up successfully.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220121500 +0000" stop="20241220125500 +0000" channel="History.ee"><title lang="ee">Ancient Aliens</title><desc lang="ee">ANCIENT ALIENS examines 75 million years of the most credible alien evidence here on Earth, from the age of the dinosaurs, to ancient Egypt, to the skies over the western desert in the present day US. Ancient cave drawings of strange creatures, an asphalt-like substance in an Egyptian pyramid made from the remains of unidentified creatures, continued mass sightings in the USA -- these are just a few of the strange stories that will be investigated.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220125500 +0000" stop="20241220134000 +0000" channel="History.ee"><title lang="ee">The UnXplained with William Shatner</title><desc lang="ee">From the producers of Ancient Aliens® and The Curse of Oak Island® From alleged UFO encounters to sudden disappearances to evil possessions, series host William Shatner attempts to get to the truth behind the most bizarre and mysterious events ever reported. With the help of the world&apos;s top scientists, first-hand &quot;experiencer&quot; accounts, and dramatic reenactments, viewers gain shocking insight into what&apos;s really happening--and why.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220134000 +0000" stop="20241220142000 +0000" channel="History.ee"><title lang="ee">The Proof Is Out There</title><desc lang="ee">Is a photograph of a UFO hovering over Holloman Air Force Base in New Mexico confirmation that President Eisenhower had a Top-Secret meeting with aliens there? What is the origin of frightening howls recorded in Witset, British Columbia?</desc></programme>
