<programme start="20241220040000 +0000" stop="20241220050000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Blood Relatives</title><desc lang="ee">It is often easy to regard other families as picture perfect, harmonious examples of pillars of the community. But sometimes, these facades hide dreadful criminal intent and gruesome violence. Brenda Strong narrates this show which exposes murderous secrets hidden within the family unit. Each epsiode explores a separate story involving a family tragedy and reveals the motives of other family members who are potential suspects in the crime. From sibling rivalry to conflicts over money to jealousy and infidelity, there are many factors involved which can lead to a family member paying the ultimate price. The skilled story-telling will draw the viewer in and keep them on the edge of their seat as they try to guess who the killer is.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Deadliest Mums &amp; Dads</title><desc lang="ee">When a father is confronted by police in a custody dispute, he kills nine of his children to stop his secrets being exposed. His son recalls that awful day.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Deadliest Families</title><desc lang="ee">In October 2022, 36-year-old Angie White is found dead at her home in Wales. Alexa recordings from the night of her murder help catch her killer.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220080000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Dead Of Winter</title><desc lang="ee">True-crime documentary series that tells the true stories of murders which occured in wintry conditions and the cruelest environments, using winter as a living and breathing malevolent character. Each episode shows how the detectives worked to track down a killer, all while battling the unforgiving elements. The series features interviews with family and investigators, and dramatic re-enactments of some shocking cases such as the case of Linda Velzy, who vanished after Christmas shopping in 1977, case of the disappearance of Dean Fawcett, the murder of Virginia Johannessen, and others.</desc></programme>
