<programme start="20241220130000 +0000" stop="20241220140000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Evil Stepmothers</title><desc lang="ee">True crime series. When parents separate or divorce it is always tough for the children. So when a father finds a new partner and welcomes her to the family, how can you be sure if she is as amiable as first appearances suggest? These harrowing real stories, along with re-enactments, reveal how step-mothers can change from friendly parental figures, to abusive and even murderous family members. Featuring tales from across the United States, these brutal and vicious women make Cineralla&apos;s stepmother look like a saint, and truly support the old saying: you can&apos;t judge a book by its cover.</desc></programme>
