<programme start="20241220170000 +0000" stop="20241220180000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Relatively Evil</title><desc lang="ee">Documentary series that features six terrifying cases of family dynamics turning deadly. &apos;&apos;Relatively evil&apos;&apos; explores the real-life stories of outsiders who fell in love with someone in a seemingly normal family but soon found themselves entangled with an evil clan capable of abuse, kidnapping, or something even more sinister. Each episode features a true crime murder mystery where the pool of suspects are all from within the family.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220180000 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.ee"><title lang="ee">Evil Kin</title><desc lang="ee">There are many inheritable traits about a person, maybe you have your fathers nose, or your uncles talent for guitar? But, what if the things you pull from your family gene pool aren&apos;t as positive, what if you gain a particular penchant for something like... murder? This series delves into the possibility that evil is inheritable and that bad blood runs through a family, looking into cases where relatives have gone on a rampage and mothers have helped to murder. It&apos;s a terrifying and twisted thought, but it&apos;s a likely idea that has too much evidence to deny. Follow along and decide for yourself, can one family harness so much evil and call it a coincidence?</desc></programme>
