<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Deadliest Mums &amp; Dads</title><desc lang="lv">When a father is confronted by police in a custody dispute, he kills nine of his children to stop his secrets being exposed. His son recalls that awful day.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Deadliest Families</title><desc lang="lv">In October 2022, 36-year-old Angie White is found dead at her home in Wales. Alexa recordings from the night of her murder help catch her killer.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220080000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Dead Of Winter</title><desc lang="lv">True-crime documentary series that tells the true stories of murders which occured in wintry conditions and the cruelest environments, using winter as a living and breathing malevolent character. Each episode shows how the detectives worked to track down a killer, all while battling the unforgiving elements. The series features interviews with family and investigators, and dramatic re-enactments of some shocking cases such as the case of Linda Velzy, who vanished after Christmas shopping in 1977, case of the disappearance of Dean Fawcett, the murder of Virginia Johannessen, and others.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220080000 +0000" stop="20241220090000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Dead Of Winter</title><desc lang="lv">True-crime documentary series that tells the true stories of murders which occured in wintry conditions and the cruelest environments, using winter as a living and breathing malevolent character. Each episode shows how the detectives worked to track down a killer, all while battling the unforgiving elements. The series features interviews with family and investigators, and dramatic re-enactments of some shocking cases such as the case of Linda Velzy, who vanished after Christmas shopping in 1977, case of the disappearance of Dean Fawcett, the murder of Virginia Johannessen, and others.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220090000 +0000" stop="20241220110000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">The Madeleine McCann Mystery</title><desc lang="lv">When three-year-old Madeleine McCann disappeared from her holiday apartment in 2007, it shocked the world. Still unsolved, new analysis is made to try and discover the truth.</desc></programme>
