<programme start="20241220130000 +0000" stop="20241220140000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Evil Stepmothers</title><desc lang="lv">True crime series. When parents separate or divorce it is always tough for the children. So when a father finds a new partner and welcomes her to the family, how can you be sure if she is as amiable as first appearances suggest? These harrowing real stories, along with re-enactments, reveal how step-mothers can change from friendly parental figures, to abusive and even murderous family members. Featuring tales from across the United States, these brutal and vicious women make Cineralla&apos;s stepmother look like a saint, and truly support the old saying: you can&apos;t judge a book by its cover.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220140000 +0000" stop="20241220150000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Evil Stepmothers</title><desc lang="lv">True crime series. When parents separate or divorce it is always tough for the children. So when a father finds a new partner and welcomes her to the family, how can you be sure if she is as amiable as first appearances suggest? These harrowing real stories, along with re-enactments, reveal how step-mothers can change from friendly parental figures, to abusive and even murderous family members. Featuring tales from across the United States, these brutal and vicious women make Cineralla&apos;s stepmother look like a saint, and truly support the old saying: you can&apos;t judge a book by its cover.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220150000 +0000" stop="20241220170000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Mother, May I Murder?</title><desc lang="lv">The mysterious disappearance of a New York millionaire and a plan to steal an $8 million townhouse unearths an unbelievable story and two con artists.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220170000 +0000" stop="20241220180000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Relatively Evil</title><desc lang="lv">Documentary series that features six terrifying cases of family dynamics turning deadly. &apos;&apos;Relatively evil&apos;&apos; explores the real-life stories of outsiders who fell in love with someone in a seemingly normal family but soon found themselves entangled with an evil clan capable of abuse, kidnapping, or something even more sinister. Each episode features a true crime murder mystery where the pool of suspects are all from within the family.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220180000 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Evil Kin</title><desc lang="lv">There are many inheritable traits about a person, maybe you have your fathers nose, or your uncles talent for guitar? But, what if the things you pull from your family gene pool aren&apos;t as positive, what if you gain a particular penchant for something like... murder? This series delves into the possibility that evil is inheritable and that bad blood runs through a family, looking into cases where relatives have gone on a rampage and mothers have helped to murder. It&apos;s a terrifying and twisted thought, but it&apos;s a likely idea that has too much evidence to deny. Follow along and decide for yourself, can one family harness so much evil and call it a coincidence?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220200000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">The Wonderland Murders</title><desc lang="lv">In the Pacific Northwest of the United States lies an area dubbed Wonderland, aptly titled due to its natural beauty and picturesque landscapes. Underneath the idyllic facade, there is a dark, sinister connection to gruesome murders and sinister serial killers, who see the unspoiled natural haven as the perfect place to kill innocent civilians, or simply hide their victim&apos;s bodies. This documentary series explores chilling tales from across the area, using dramatic reconstructions, archived footage and interviews with those involved to reveal the dangers that lie in the shadows of Wonderland.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220200000 +0000" stop="20241220210000 +0000" channel="InvestigationDiscovery.lv"><title lang="lv">Married To Evil</title><desc lang="lv">A figure dressed as a clown shoots a mother on her doorstep. The case goes cold until an unexpected break helps bring the killer clown to justice.</desc></programme>
