<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220063000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Stoked</title><desc lang="ee">Captivating animated series that folllows the lives of six teenagers who all share love for surfing and spend their summer working at Surfer&apos;s Paradise Ridgemount Resort, in British Columbia. Meet Emma, Reef and Fin who join locals Broseph, Lo, and Johnny, and hope they will have the summer of their lives, working at the famous Surfer&apos;s Paradise Hotel. They will be more that surprised when they find out that their jobs are awful, as they have to deal with ugly uniforms, bad working hours, house that is in terrible shape and the manager who isn&apos;t the nicest of people. However, things are not so bad, as they get the opportunity to do the thing they love the most- surf, on their days off.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220063000 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Bunk&apos;d</title><desc lang="ee">Bunk&apos;d shows Ravi Ross and his sisters Emma and Zuri who decide to leave noisy streets of New York and set off to a rustic summer camp Kikiwaka in Maine where their parents met as teenagers. The camp got its name after a magic creature Kikiwaka that leaves nearby. From the first minutes of their stay guys realize that holidays are not going to be easy and relaxing, as the head of Kikiwaka turns out to remember their Mom who stole her boyfriend. That boyfriend later became the father of the three. Plus the conditions in the camp are very specific and far from perfect, health code and safety regulations are seriously violated. Ravi has a weird roommate, Zuri&apos;s roommate is a nerd, so kids start to doubt whether it is worth staying. Also modern technologies like phones and notebooks are not available in the camp, which makes it even harder. Fortunately the teens are smart enough to figure out their way out of the most difficult and strange situations.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220073000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">K.C. Undercover</title><desc lang="ee">Fascinating spy series K.C. Undercover shows intriguing story of K.C. Cooper, a high school student. Just like other teenagers K.C. goes to school, does homework and wonders about her future. Her life changes drastically after she finds out that her parents are professional secret agents. K.C. wants to follow their steps and after getting their approval gets her first serious task. The main character shows both sides of her life- regular life with troubles at home and secret missions, aimed at country&apos;s rescue, sometimes rescue of the whole humankind.</desc></programme>
