<programme start="20241220083000 +0000" stop="20241220084500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Hoodie</title><desc lang="ee">Hoodie is a superhero story about a perfectly normal boy, with an exceptional talent for parkour and a passion for justice. For two years now, he has been practising parkour with Soufian, the best tracer in Brussels. In secret, as his mother, a passionate police officer, would never approve it. When three neighbourhood kids, Flo, Basim and Kenza, discover Pieter&apos;s talent and motivation, they join him to become an unexpected superhero crew: Team Hoodie. They are connected by one goal: to liberate the neighbourhood from injustice.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220084500 +0000" stop="20241220091500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Power Rangers Dino Charge</title><desc lang="ee">In this children&apos;s series, based on a prehistoric Earth where an alien entrusted powerful Energems to 10 dinosaurs, but when the dinosaurs went extinct, the Energems were lost. Now an intergalactic bounty hunter is determined to reclaim the Energems and destroy our planet. A new team of Power Rangers must find the lost Energems and use their Dino Chargers to power up a dino-fueled battle gear, Zords and Megazords to save the world. Will the Power Rangers be able to save our planet?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220091500 +0000" stop="20241220093000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Polly Pocket</title><desc lang="ee">Often told she is too little to do all the things she wants to do, Polly doesn&apos;t let this stand in her way and proves what every kid should know... that being little isn&apos;t a limitation. Instead, its her greatest strength! Inheriting a magic locket that allows her to shrink to only 4 inches tall, she discovers that no matter how small she is, she can still have big adventures and create a big difference for her and her best friends! Based on the famous Polly Pocket doll, this Canadian-American animation TV series features 26 episodes of big adventures, lots of imagination and even more fun!</desc></programme>
