<programme start="20241220110000 +0000" stop="20241220113000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Heidi</title><desc lang="ee">Heidi is a little girl who is full of beans. She faces many problems up in the Swiss alps whilst living with her grandfather. Heidi lights up and soothes the people and animals all around her, with her enthusiastic, generous and wonderful zest for life. This bubbly, young orphan girl will learn the priceless value of friendship and mutual respect. Follow her journey as she discovers life&apos;s ups and downs.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220113000 +0000" stop="20241220120000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Barbie: A Touch of Magic</title><desc lang="ee">Barbie &quot;Malibu&quot; Roberts and Barbie &quot;Brooklyn&quot; Roberts discover a mysterious baby Pegasus on the beach in Malibu and work to find out where the magical horse came from. While they try to find out how to get little Peggy home, Malibu and Brooklyn, with the help of Malibu&apos;s sisters and best friend Ken, have to protect their four-legged friend from a Glyph, the fantastical creature that followed Peggy in hopes of stealing the little horse&apos;s wings.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220120000 +0000" stop="20241220121500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Polly Pocket</title><desc lang="ee">Often told she is too little to do all the things she wants to do, Polly doesn&apos;t let this stand in her way and proves what every kid should know... that being little isn&apos;t a limitation. Instead, its her greatest strength! Inheriting a magic locket that allows her to shrink to only 4 inches tall, she discovers that no matter how small she is, she can still have big adventures and create a big difference for her and her best friends! Based on the famous Polly Pocket doll, this Canadian-American animation TV series features 26 episodes of big adventures, lots of imagination and even more fun!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220121500 +0000" stop="20241220123000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Zoom the White Dolphin</title><desc lang="ee">A thirteen-year-old Jean and his little sister Marina live on an exotic island with their uncle Patrick. One day they meet and a white dolphin named Oum. They make friends, Oum is an extremely intelligent animal. Together they have numerous exciting adventures. There are several other animals, who have fun with them- a mynah bird, a koala, and a sloth.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220123000 +0000" stop="20241220124500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Zoom the White Dolphin</title><desc lang="ee">A thirteen-year-old Jean and his little sister Marina live on an exotic island with their uncle Patrick. One day they meet and a white dolphin named Oum. They make friends, Oum is an extremely intelligent animal. Together they have numerous exciting adventures. There are several other animals, who have fun with them- a mynah bird, a koala, and a sloth.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220124500 +0000" stop="20241220131500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Ninjago: Dragons Rising</title><desc lang="ee">Computer-animated epic fantasy superhero sequel series. It&apos;s dragons versus Photac beasts in the streets of Imperium, but the Claws stop Lloyd and Wyldfyre&apos;s efforts to free the escaped dragons as Sora and Arin search for Riyu. The young dragon&apos;s spark would allow Sora to shut down the Photacs for good - unfortunately, the Teen Protection Force brings him before the Empress... Meanwhile, Nya and Kai reunite under mysterious circumstances and face an apparition.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220131500 +0000" stop="20241220134500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Beyblade X</title><desc lang="ee">A young boy who aims to be a professional Beyblade player. He aims to get to X Tower, where professional Beyblade players gather.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220134500 +0000" stop="20241220140000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Sisters</title><desc lang="ee">Comedy animation about two close siblings, both with big characters, who are at the same time both best friends and each other&apos;s biggest enemy. Wendy is a 13-year-old girl who likes to listen to music, use her phone and hang out with her boyfriend. Wendy is eager to be grown up and mature. But her energetic little sister, Marine, is often close by with a headful of crazy ideas. Wendy is irritated by Marine and the invasion of her privacy. But although they can fight, as sisters do, they are very loyal to each other and always make up in the end.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220140000 +0000" stop="20241220141500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Boy Girl Dog Cat Mouse Cheese</title><desc lang="ee">Meet the unique and a slightly dysfunctional family. A group that consist of a boy, the oldest in the family who is a bit anxious, a girl who is rebellious, and a dog, a cat who behaves bizarrely, a mouse who is highly intelligent and anthropomorphic cheese who is drama queen makes a rather strange and quirky blended family. They have crazy adventures all the time as they must learn to love each other and live together under the same roof.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220141500 +0000" stop="20241220143000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Boy Girl Dog Cat Mouse Cheese</title><desc lang="ee">Lila has a brand new vlog that goes viral in school. Her life just looks so interesting! Naturally Girl doesn&apos;t like seeing her nasty rival have such success, so Girl begins filming her own vlog about her family&apos;s real life. The kids have fun doing it, and they begin to beat Lila&apos;s viewer count. But when Lila counters with a super amazing vlog, Girl thinks the only way to top her is by scripting stories to make her family more interesting. Unfortunately the kids don&apos;t like being fake, so they angrily drop out of the project, meaning Girl may never beat Lila! But what&apos;s more important - a silly rivalry or her silly family?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220143000 +0000" stop="20241220150000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Stoked</title><desc lang="ee">Captivating animated series that folllows the lives of six teenagers who all share love for surfing and spend their summer working at Surfer&apos;s Paradise Ridgemount Resort, in British Columbia. Meet Emma, Reef and Fin who join locals Broseph, Lo, and Johnny, and hope they will have the summer of their lives, working at the famous Surfer&apos;s Paradise Hotel. They will be more that surprised when they find out that their jobs are awful, as they have to deal with ugly uniforms, bad working hours, house that is in terrible shape and the manager who isn&apos;t the nicest of people. However, things are not so bad, as they get the opportunity to do the thing they love the most- surf, on their days off.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220150000 +0000" stop="20241220153000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">K.C. Undercover</title><desc lang="ee">Fascinating spy series K.C. Undercover shows intriguing story of K.C. Cooper, a high school student. Just like other teenagers K.C. goes to school, does homework and wonders about her future. Her life changes drastically after she finds out that her parents are professional secret agents. K.C. wants to follow their steps and after getting their approval gets her first serious task. The main character shows both sides of her life- regular life with troubles at home and secret missions, aimed at country&apos;s rescue, sometimes rescue of the whole humankind.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220153000 +0000" stop="20241220160000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Bunk&apos;d</title><desc lang="ee">Bunk&apos;d shows Ravi Ross and his sisters Emma and Zuri who decide to leave noisy streets of New York and set off to a rustic summer camp Kikiwaka in Maine where their parents met as teenagers. The camp got its name after a magic creature Kikiwaka that leaves nearby. From the first minutes of their stay guys realize that holidays are not going to be easy and relaxing, as the head of Kikiwaka turns out to remember their Mom who stole her boyfriend. That boyfriend later became the father of the three. Plus the conditions in the camp are very specific and far from perfect, health code and safety regulations are seriously violated. Ravi has a weird roommate, Zuri&apos;s roommate is a nerd, so kids start to doubt whether it is worth staying. Also modern technologies like phones and notebooks are not available in the camp, which makes it even harder. Fortunately the teens are smart enough to figure out their way out of the most difficult and strange situations.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220160000 +0000" stop="20241220163000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">100% Wolf</title><desc lang="ee">Freddy Lupin knows he&apos;s got what it takes to run with the elite werewolf Night Patrol. All he has to do is win a place at the prestigious Howlington Academy, keep his fluffy butt out of trouble and graduate. Easy, right? WRONG! Being the first dog at a werewolf-only finishing school is tougher than Freddy ever imagined.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220163000 +0000" stop="20241220170000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.ee"><title lang="ee">Lego DREAMZzz</title><desc lang="ee">With realms going missing, the dream chasers feel like they should be taking the fight to the Never Witch instead of training for R.E.M. trials, which isn&apos;t going well either. Zoey&apos;s haunted by her most painful memories and Mateo continues to only dream craft Z-Blob-related items. The Night Hunter, now forced to work for the Never Witch, mysteriously keeps tabs on the kids in the waking world.</desc></programme>
