<programme start="20241220073000 +0000" stop="20241220075500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">100% Wolf</title><desc lang="lv">Freddy Lupin knows he&apos;s got what it takes to run with the elite werewolf Night Patrol. All he has to do is win a place at the prestigious Howlington Academy, keep his fluffy butt out of trouble and graduate. Easy, right? WRONG! Being the first dog at a werewolf-only finishing school is tougher than Freddy ever imagined.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220075500 +0000" stop="20241220081000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Hoodie</title><desc lang="lv">Hoodie is a superhero story about a perfectly normal boy, with an exceptional talent for parkour and a passion for justice. For two years now, he has been practising parkour with Soufian, the best tracer in Brussels. In secret, as his mother, a passionate police officer, would never approve it. When three neighbourhood kids, Flo, Basim and Kenza, discover Pieter&apos;s talent and motivation, they join him to become an unexpected superhero crew: Team Hoodie. They are connected by one goal: to liberate the neighbourhood from injustice.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220081000 +0000" stop="20241220083500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Power Rangers Dino Charge</title><desc lang="lv">In this children&apos;s series, based on a prehistoric Earth where an alien entrusted powerful Energems to 10 dinosaurs, but when the dinosaurs went extinct, the Energems were lost. Now an intergalactic bounty hunter is determined to reclaim the Energems and destroy our planet. A new team of Power Rangers must find the lost Energems and use their Dino Chargers to power up a dino-fueled battle gear, Zords and Megazords to save the world. Will the Power Rangers be able to save our planet?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220083500 +0000" stop="20241220085000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Horrid Henry</title><desc lang="lv">Horrid Henry is always getting in trouble. He is a head strong, prankster with a strong disregard for authority. His selfish ways cause chaos wherever he goes, and he is relentless when it comes to outsmarting enemies, teachers, babysitters, or pretty much any adult. And to make matters worse Henry&apos;s little brother Peter is Perfect. Whilst Henry never seems to learn from his Horrid behvaiour, Perfect Peter&apos;s gets more perfect every day.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220085000 +0000" stop="20241220091500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Stoked</title><desc lang="lv">Captivating animated series that folllows the lives of six teenagers who all share love for surfing and spend their summer working at Surfer&apos;s Paradise Ridgemount Resort, in British Columbia. Meet Emma, Reef and Fin who join locals Broseph, Lo, and Johnny, and hope they will have the summer of their lives, working at the famous Surfer&apos;s Paradise Hotel. They will be more that surprised when they find out that their jobs are awful, as they have to deal with ugly uniforms, bad working hours, house that is in terrible shape and the manager who isn&apos;t the nicest of people. However, things are not so bad, as they get the opportunity to do the thing they love the most- surf, on their days off.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220091500 +0000" stop="20241220093000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Polly Pocket</title><desc lang="lv">Often told she is too little to do all the things she wants to do, Polly doesn&apos;t let this stand in her way and proves what every kid should know... that being little isn&apos;t a limitation. Instead, its her greatest strength! Inheriting a magic locket that allows her to shrink to only 4 inches tall, she discovers that no matter how small she is, she can still have big adventures and create a big difference for her and her best friends! Based on the famous Polly Pocket doll, this Canadian-American animation TV series features 26 episodes of big adventures, lots of imagination and even more fun!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220093000 +0000" stop="20241220095500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Barbie: A Touch of Magic</title><desc lang="lv">Barbie &quot;Malibu&quot; Roberts and Barbie &quot;Brooklyn&quot; Roberts discover a mysterious baby Pegasus on the beach in Malibu and work to find out where the magical horse came from. While they try to find out how to get little Peggy home, Malibu and Brooklyn, with the help of Malibu&apos;s sisters and best friend Ken, have to protect their four-legged friend from a Glyph, the fantastical creature that followed Peggy in hopes of stealing the little horse&apos;s wings.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220095500 +0000" stop="20241220101000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Zoom the White Dolphin</title><desc lang="lv">A thirteen-year-old Jean and his little sister Marina live on an exotic island with their uncle Patrick. One day they meet and a white dolphin named Oum. They make friends, Oum is an extremely intelligent animal. Together they have numerous exciting adventures. There are several other animals, who have fun with them- a mynah bird, a koala, and a sloth.</desc></programme>
