<programme start="20241220102000 +0000" stop="20241220103500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Tobot: Daedo&apos;s Heroes</title><desc lang="lv">It&apos;s been two years since the disappearance of the villainous robot army. During that time, the Tobots have become legends and are no longer needed. Ryan, Kory, and Dylan have headed into Fifth Grade, and Franklin (Ryan and Kory&apos;s dad) and Limo (Dylan&apos;s dad) run an auto repair shop together. But when new villainous robots and an evil mastermind appear, the peace of the city is threatend and the Tobots are forced to get back in the game.</desc></programme>
