<programme start="20241220135000 +0000" stop="20241220140500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Transformers: Cyberverse</title><desc lang="lv">Bumblebee receives an important task, several lives depend on him but the problem is that he has forgotten everything! It&apos;s a good thing that his friend and partner Windblade comes to the rescue and helps him repair his damaged memory files. Each new memory reopens Bumblebee&apos;s past adventures on Cybertron, before arrival to Earth. He experiences fun moments with his friends all over again, moments that changed his life. This past has made him the hero we all know. Each step in fighting Bumblebee&apos;s amnesia provides new tips to the friends, so sooner or later it will help them perform their mission and stay away from trouble.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220140500 +0000" stop="20241220142000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Boy Girl Dog Cat Mouse Cheese</title><desc lang="lv">One day the kids answer the door to meet Wedgie. She&apos;s Cheese&apos;s missing piece from the lab experiment that brought them both to life! Wedgie is happy to have finally found her family, and the kids happily take her in. But when Wedgie &quot;out cutes&quot; Cheese, Cheese gets way too jealous! The kids tell Cheese to knock it off, but things only get worse when Wedgie starts framing Cheese for bad things! When confronted, Cheese maintains innocence, but they don&apos;t believe her! What is going on?! And is Wedgie all she appears to be?!</desc></programme>
