<programme start="20241221043000 +0000" stop="20241221044500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMax.lv"><title lang="lv">Zoom the White Dolphin</title><desc lang="lv">A thirteen-year-old Jean and his little sister Marina live on an exotic island with their uncle Patrick. One day they meet and a white dolphin named Oum. They make friends, Oum is an extremely intelligent animal. Together they have numerous exciting adventures. There are several other animals, who have fun with them- a mynah bird, a koala, and a sloth.</desc></programme>
