<programme start="20241220053000 +0000" stop="20241220054500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Pikwik Pack</title><desc lang="ee">Pikwik Pack follows four adorable animals, Suki the hedgehog, Axel the raccoon, Tibor the hippo and Hazel the cat as they deliver magical packages filled with love to the kind citizens of Pikwik. Every day, a new surprise package arrives. The team might face rough rapids, stormy skies, or a foggy forest, but when they work together, they always deliver! The series is packed with big adventures, silly hijinks, and heartfelt charm that will entertain preschoolers while underscoring the value of community, responsibility and teamwork.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220054500 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Remy &amp; Boo</title><desc lang="ee">This children&apos;s animation follows the adventures of Remy, a six-year-old girl, and her unusual best friend, Boo, a large, mushy, pink robot. Combining Remy&apos;s invincible and courageous attitude and Boo&apos;s gung-ho spirit, the duo enjoy many fun-filled and exciting exploits in Dolphin Bay. The charming and humorous stories reveal the importance and power of having meaningful friendships. Among many of the subjects covered, episodes touch on issues such as trust, helping others, overcoming difficulties, curiosity, bravery, and being creative.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220061000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Bluey</title><desc lang="ee">Bluey is Australian TV animated series, the main character is a Blue Heeler puppy named Bluey, he lives with his family: father Bandit, mother Chilli and his younger sister Bingo. It is worthy of note that Blue Heeler is an Australian breed that is in top ten according to intelligence level. Bluey is a tireless, smart, quick puppy, extremely curious in everything that is going on around him. Bingo is always by his side in his adventures. Bluey&apos;s family relationship is very warm, supportive and realistic, that arouses additional interest in this series. This kind of family reminds us of our own families or of the ones we want to have. Each story is an emotional true event from everyday real life with its own drama, lessons and conclusions.</desc></programme>
