<programme start="20241220063000 +0000" stop="20241220064500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Tobot: Daedo&apos;s Heroes</title><desc lang="ee">It&apos;s been two years since the disappearance of the villainous robot army. During that time, the Tobots have become legends and are no longer needed. Ryan, Kory, and Dylan have headed into Fifth Grade, and Franklin (Ryan and Kory&apos;s dad) and Limo (Dylan&apos;s dad) run an auto repair shop together. But when new villainous robots and an evil mastermind appear, the peace of the city is threatend and the Tobots are forced to get back in the game.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220064500 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Dino Ranch</title><desc lang="ee">Follow the amazing animated adventures of the Cassidy family, who live in &apos;&apos;Dino Ranch&apos;&apos;, a special and unique ranch in which dinosaurs roam freely. Meet Bo and Jane Cassidy and their children Jon, Min, and Miguel, and join them as they help dinos and have lots of fun along the way.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220071500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Super Wings!</title><desc lang="ee">Jett and Paul head to Saint Gallen, Switzerland and deliver a gingerbread man costume that emits the smell of freshly— baked gingerbread cookies. / Jett and Mira fly to San Cristobal, Ecuador to deliver super strong bubble solution. The package is for a boy who wants to blow super strong bubbles that will last and last. / When a girl named Sylviya asks for a special watering can for her flowers, Jett and Dizzy head to Bulgaria. This leads to an encounter with bees and a new Super Wing named Bucky. / A young boy named Gio asks the Super Wings to build him a special suit to wear to the local Mud Festival that will protect him from getting muddy. / A young boy in Denmark orders egg capsules to hold three baby &quot;block&quot; dinosaurs he invented. He wants to present the eggs to their mothers in Blockosaurs Park.</desc></programme>
