<programme start="20241220073000 +0000" stop="20241220080000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Gabby&apos;s Dollhouse</title><desc lang="ee">With a little magic and a daily dollhouse delivery, explore the fantastical dollhouse with Gabby and all her kitty friends. Gabby is a positive and determined 11-year-old girl who embraces imperfection and turns mistakes into growth. Her best friend Pandy Paws is always by her side, ready for any adventure with a snack and a smile. Come along with them and the other Gabby Cats on quirky adventures, and play, craft, dance and discover new things every day!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220080000 +0000" stop="20241220081000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Paprika</title><desc lang="ee">The Paprika Twins Stan and Olivia live on an imaginative island and are always looking to make their day more exciting. The energetic duo never let anything get in their way, not even Stan&apos;s wheelchair. Supported by their friends Big foot, Puff, Podium and Magma the Paprika twins can turn any boring day into a wild adventure, making friends and singing songs along the way. Stan has a disability and can be recognised by his wheelchair doubles, which allow Olivia to tag along without having to run alongside him meaning they can always stick together. The almost identical twins couldn&apos;t be more different, However their differences is exactly why they&apos;re such a perfectly balanced duo.</desc></programme>
