<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220190800 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.ee"><title lang="ee">Peppa Pig</title><desc lang="ee">Adorable Peppa Pig is admired not only by kids but also by adults all over the world. Peppa lives together with her family, George Pig-her little brother, Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig. Peppa likes to jump in muddy puddles and play with her best friend Suzy Ship. George is too small, he barely talks, he never separates from his toy dinosaur. Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig are loving and caring parents, they go to work every day. Whether they&apos;re playing games, going to the playground or visiting their cousins, Peppa and her family are there to educate on everything life-related.</desc></programme>
