<programme start="20241220052800 +0000" stop="20241220053000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Peppa Pig</title><desc lang="lv">Adorable Peppa Pig is admired not only by kids but also by adults all over the world. Peppa lives together with her family, George Pig-her little brother, Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig. Peppa likes to jump in muddy puddles and play with her best friend Suzy Ship. George is too small, he barely talks, he never separates from his toy dinosaur. Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig are loving and caring parents, they go to work every day. Whether they&apos;re playing games, going to the playground or visiting their cousins, Peppa and her family are there to educate on everything life-related.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220053000 +0000" stop="20241220054000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Adventures of Little Penguin</title><desc lang="lv">Oscar and Leah join Nimit and Pranit in the nearby penguin village. But the two monkeys are very playful and still very noisy. The local Mayor sends them off to cool down. Oscar joins them to keep company. Meanwhile, back in the village, Emile, the hungry Leopard Sealion, is once again on the attack, this time with Leah in harm&apos;s way! Oscar and the monkeys hurry back to save the day with a bit of help from a lot of bananas. And Nimit and Pranit are forgiven.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220054000 +0000" stop="20241220054900 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Adventures of Little Penguin</title><desc lang="lv">It is the day before the big Cherry Blossom Festival, and everyone in the small penguin village is hoping that their two prized trees will win. But during the night, they are stolen. Oscar, Leah, Nimit, and Pranit follow the trail to a nearby town. And El Vis is once again up to no good; the gang of sheep is the thieves. Armed with imagination and big springs, our friends make a daring getaway with the trees like no one has seen before!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220054900 +0000" stop="20241220060100 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Remy &amp; Boo</title><desc lang="lv">This children&apos;s animation follows the adventures of Remy, a six-year-old girl, and her unusual best friend, Boo, a large, mushy, pink robot. Combining Remy&apos;s invincible and courageous attitude and Boo&apos;s gung-ho spirit, the duo enjoy many fun-filled and exciting exploits in Dolphin Bay. The charming and humorous stories reveal the importance and power of having meaningful friendships. Among many of the subjects covered, episodes touch on issues such as trust, helping others, overcoming difficulties, curiosity, bravery, and being creative.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060100 +0000" stop="20241220061000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Thomas &amp; Friends</title><desc lang="lv">Thomas and Friends presents life on Island of Sodor somewhere in Britain. There are several railways where all machines are animate creatures, they live and work there. Each of them tries to perform their job perfectly. The main character is a little blue tank engine Thomas, who travels to different places, gets to know different people and helps everybody who need it. Sometimes Thomas makes mistakes but it only teaches him not to repeat them in future. His friends are as hardworking as he is. Thomas and his team deliver mails, repair railway, take passengers wherever they need. Thomas and Friends can teach young viewers significant lessons of true value of friendship and importance of teamwork.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220061000 +0000" stop="20241220062500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Pikwik Pack</title><desc lang="lv">Pikwik Pack follows four adorable animals, Suki the hedgehog, Axel the raccoon, Tibor the hippo and Hazel the cat as they deliver magical packages filled with love to the kind citizens of Pikwik. Every day, a new surprise package arrives. The team might face rough rapids, stormy skies, or a foggy forest, but when they work together, they always deliver! The series is packed with big adventures, silly hijinks, and heartfelt charm that will entertain preschoolers while underscoring the value of community, responsibility and teamwork.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220062500 +0000" stop="20241220065100 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Tree Fu Tom</title><desc lang="lv">Visit the enchanted kingdom located in a tree in our hero, Tom&apos;s, backyard. Tom is blessed with the magic movement power of &quot;tree fu&quot; which transforms him into a &quot;treeling&quot; and he is transported to Treetopolis. There, along with his friends Twigs, Arilea and Zigzoo, he revels in adventures and mishaps often involving the troublesome Mushas who enjoy causing chaos for their neighbours. Tom usually has to rely on the help of the viewer to save the day as they perform their own &quot;tree fu&quot; moves and transfer the magic through the screen. As well as providing social development benefits to children, the show specifically encourages the kids to partake in therapeutic movements involving sweeping arms, stomping feet, and the clenching and relaxing of fists which keep kids engaged and physically active.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220065100 +0000" stop="20241220070500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Tobot: Daedo&apos;s Heroes</title><desc lang="lv">It&apos;s been two years since the disappearance of the villainous robot army. During that time, the Tobots have become legends and are no longer needed. Ryan, Kory, and Dylan have headed into Fifth Grade, and Franklin (Ryan and Kory&apos;s dad) and Limo (Dylan&apos;s dad) run an auto repair shop together. But when new villainous robots and an evil mastermind appear, the peace of the city is threatend and the Tobots are forced to get back in the game.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070500 +0000" stop="20241220072000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Dino Ranch</title><desc lang="lv">Follow the amazing animated adventures of the Cassidy family, who live in &apos;&apos;Dino Ranch&apos;&apos;, a special and unique ranch in which dinosaurs roam freely. Meet Bo and Jane Cassidy and their children Jon, Min, and Miguel, and join them as they help dinos and have lots of fun along the way.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220072000 +0000" stop="20241220073400 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Super Wings!</title><desc lang="lv">Jett and Paul head to Saint Gallen, Switzerland and deliver a gingerbread man costume that emits the smell of freshly— baked gingerbread cookies. / Jett and Mira fly to San Cristobal, Ecuador to deliver super strong bubble solution. The package is for a boy who wants to blow super strong bubbles that will last and last. / When a girl named Sylviya asks for a special watering can for her flowers, Jett and Dizzy head to Bulgaria. This leads to an encounter with bees and a new Super Wing named Bucky. / A young boy named Gio asks the Super Wings to build him a special suit to wear to the local Mud Festival that will protect him from getting muddy. / A young boy in Denmark orders egg capsules to hold three baby &quot;block&quot; dinosaurs he invented. He wants to present the eggs to their mothers in Blockosaurs Park.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220073400 +0000" stop="20241220074700 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Super Wings!</title><desc lang="lv">Jett and Paul head to Saint Gallen, Switzerland and deliver a gingerbread man costume that emits the smell of freshly— baked gingerbread cookies. / Jett and Mira fly to San Cristobal, Ecuador to deliver super strong bubble solution. The package is for a boy who wants to blow super strong bubbles that will last and last. / When a girl named Sylviya asks for a special watering can for her flowers, Jett and Dizzy head to Bulgaria. This leads to an encounter with bees and a new Super Wing named Bucky. / A young boy named Gio asks the Super Wings to build him a special suit to wear to the local Mud Festival that will protect him from getting muddy. / A young boy in Denmark orders egg capsules to hold three baby &quot;block&quot; dinosaurs he invented. He wants to present the eggs to their mothers in Blockosaurs Park.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220074700 +0000" stop="20241220081000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Gabby&apos;s Dollhouse</title><desc lang="lv">With a little magic and a daily dollhouse delivery, explore the fantastical dollhouse with Gabby and all her kitty friends. Gabby is a positive and determined 11-year-old girl who embraces imperfection and turns mistakes into growth. Her best friend Pandy Paws is always by her side, ready for any adventure with a snack and a smile. Come along with them and the other Gabby Cats on quirky adventures, and play, craft, dance and discover new things every day!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220081000 +0000" stop="20241220082000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Paprika</title><desc lang="lv">The Paprika Twins Stan and Olivia live on an imaginative island and are always looking to make their day more exciting. The energetic duo never let anything get in their way, not even Stan&apos;s wheelchair. Supported by their friends Big foot, Puff, Podium and Magma the Paprika twins can turn any boring day into a wild adventure, making friends and singing songs along the way. Stan has a disability and can be recognised by his wheelchair doubles, which allow Olivia to tag along without having to run alongside him meaning they can always stick together. The almost identical twins couldn&apos;t be more different, However their differences is exactly why they&apos;re such a perfectly balanced duo.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220082000 +0000" stop="20241220082500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Paprika</title><desc lang="lv">The Paprika Twins Stan and Olivia live on an imaginative island and are always looking to make their day more exciting. The energetic duo never let anything get in their way, not even Stan&apos;s wheelchair. Supported by their friends Big foot, Puff, Podium and Magma the Paprika twins can turn any boring day into a wild adventure, making friends and singing songs along the way. Stan has a disability and can be recognised by his wheelchair doubles, which allow Olivia to tag along without having to run alongside him meaning they can always stick together. The almost identical twins couldn&apos;t be more different, However their differences is exactly why they&apos;re such a perfectly balanced duo.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220082500 +0000" stop="20241220083500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Miniwhats</title><desc lang="lv">The MiniWhats are a joyful gang of six friends. Like most kids, they use drawings to find answers to their daily life questions… To do so, they use a magic pencil, bringing all their sketches to life. What a lucky bunch!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220083500 +0000" stop="20241220084500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Adventures of Little Penguin</title><desc lang="lv">At Nimit and Pranit&apos;s marvelous house, Oscar and Leah enjoy the quiet evening. Until they realize that someone has stolen the water from the swimming pool. The trail leads to the valley nearby, and sure enough, El Vis and his gang have big, evil plans. They use the water steam to make their giant zeppelin airborne. Like this, they can bungy jump down and steal food! Oscar folds their plans into a paper airplane, big enough to carry Leah and him! Onboard the zeppelin, they outsmart the sheep gang. And Nimit and Pranit? They take over the zeppelin to drift towards new horizons.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220084500 +0000" stop="20241220085300 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Adventures of Little Penguin</title><desc lang="lv">Oscar and Leah follow The Book of Sinoe, and it brings them to a beautiful beach. When they wake up the following day, they find themselves captured and bound among a tribe of dancing crabs! It could all be fun and friendship, but the not-so-friendly crab, Marcel, keeps animosity boiling. As Oscar teaches Vincent, the-much-more-friendly crab, how to roll back on the feet (something the crabs have been unable to do), the game changes, and Marcel must see his scheming days are over, and all the Crabs rejoice, even more, dancing.</desc></programme>
