<programme start="20241220151500 +0000" stop="20241220152500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Dino Ranch</title><desc lang="lv">Follow the amazing animated adventures of the Cassidy family, who live in &apos;&apos;Dino Ranch&apos;&apos;, a special and unique ranch in which dinosaurs roam freely. Meet Bo and Jane Cassidy and their children Jon, Min, and Miguel, and join them as they help dinos and have lots of fun along the way.</desc></programme>
