<programme start="20241220162500 +0000" stop="20241220163500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Paprika</title><desc lang="lv">The Paprika Twins Stan and Olivia live on an imaginative island and are always looking to make their day more exciting. The energetic duo never let anything get in their way, not even Stan&apos;s wheelchair. Supported by their friends Big foot, Puff, Podium and Magma the Paprika twins can turn any boring day into a wild adventure, making friends and singing songs along the way. Stan has a disability and can be recognised by his wheelchair doubles, which allow Olivia to tag along without having to run alongside him meaning they can always stick together. The almost identical twins couldn&apos;t be more different, However their differences is exactly why they&apos;re such a perfectly balanced duo.</desc></programme>
