<programme start="20241220180500 +0000" stop="20241220183200 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Tree Fu Tom</title><desc lang="lv">Visit the enchanted kingdom located in a tree in our hero, Tom&apos;s, backyard. Tom is blessed with the magic movement power of &quot;tree fu&quot; which transforms him into a &quot;treeling&quot; and he is transported to Treetopolis. There, along with his friends Twigs, Arilea and Zigzoo, he revels in adventures and mishaps often involving the troublesome Mushas who enjoy causing chaos for their neighbours. Tom usually has to rely on the help of the viewer to save the day as they perform their own &quot;tree fu&quot; moves and transfer the magic through the screen. As well as providing social development benefits to children, the show specifically encourages the kids to partake in therapeutic movements involving sweeping arms, stomping feet, and the clenching and relaxing of fists which keep kids engaged and physically active.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220183200 +0000" stop="20241220183900 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Peppa Pig</title><desc lang="lv">Adorable Peppa Pig is admired not only by kids but also by adults all over the world. Peppa lives together with her family, George Pig-her little brother, Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig. Peppa likes to jump in muddy puddles and play with her best friend Suzy Ship. George is too small, he barely talks, he never separates from his toy dinosaur. Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig are loving and caring parents, they go to work every day. Whether they&apos;re playing games, going to the playground or visiting their cousins, Peppa and her family are there to educate on everything life-related.</desc></programme>
