<programme start="20241220185800 +0000" stop="20241220191000 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Remy &amp; Boo</title><desc lang="lv">This children&apos;s animation follows the adventures of Remy, a six-year-old girl, and her unusual best friend, Boo, a large, mushy, pink robot. Combining Remy&apos;s invincible and courageous attitude and Boo&apos;s gung-ho spirit, the duo enjoy many fun-filled and exciting exploits in Dolphin Bay. The charming and humorous stories reveal the importance and power of having meaningful friendships. Among many of the subjects covered, episodes touch on issues such as trust, helping others, overcoming difficulties, curiosity, bravery, and being creative.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220191000 +0000" stop="20241220191500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Adventures of Little Penguin</title><desc lang="lv">At Nimit and Pranit&apos;s marvelous house, Oscar and Leah enjoy the quiet evening. Until they realize that someone has stolen the water from the swimming pool. The trail leads to the valley nearby, and sure enough, El Vis and his gang have big, evil plans. They use the water steam to make their giant zeppelin airborne. Like this, they can bungy jump down and steal food! Oscar folds their plans into a paper airplane, big enough to carry Leah and him! Onboard the zeppelin, they outsmart the sheep gang. And Nimit and Pranit? They take over the zeppelin to drift towards new horizons.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220191500 +0000" stop="20241220192500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">The Adventures of Little Penguin</title><desc lang="lv">Oscar and Leah follow The Book of Sinoe, and it brings them to a beautiful beach. When they wake up the following day, they find themselves captured and bound among a tribe of dancing crabs! It could all be fun and friendship, but the not-so-friendly crab, Marcel, keeps animosity boiling. As Oscar teaches Vincent, the-much-more-friendly crab, how to roll back on the feet (something the crabs have been unable to do), the game changes, and Marcel must see his scheming days are over, and all the Crabs rejoice, even more, dancing.</desc></programme>
