<programme start="20241220204200 +0000" stop="20241220205500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Thomas &amp; Friends</title><desc lang="lv">Thomas and Friends presents life on Island of Sodor somewhere in Britain. There are several railways where all machines are animate creatures, they live and work there. Each of them tries to perform their job perfectly. The main character is a little blue tank engine Thomas, who travels to different places, gets to know different people and helps everybody who need it. Sometimes Thomas makes mistakes but it only teaches him not to repeat them in future. His friends are as hardworking as he is. Thomas and his team deliver mails, repair railway, take passengers wherever they need. Thomas and Friends can teach young viewers significant lessons of true value of friendship and importance of teamwork.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220205500 +0000" stop="20241220210500 +0000" channel="KidZoneMini.lv"><title lang="lv">Pikwik Pack</title><desc lang="lv">Pikwik Pack follows four adorable animals, Suki the hedgehog, Axel the raccoon, Tibor the hippo and Hazel the cat as they deliver magical packages filled with love to the kind citizens of Pikwik. Every day, a new surprise package arrives. The team might face rough rapids, stormy skies, or a foggy forest, but when they work together, they always deliver! The series is packed with big adventures, silly hijinks, and heartfelt charm that will entertain preschoolers while underscoring the value of community, responsibility and teamwork.</desc></programme>
