<programme start="20241220133000 +0000" stop="20241220141500 +0000" channel="NationalGeographicWild.ee"><title lang="ee">The Incredible Dr. Pol</title><desc lang="ee">Reality show follows Dutch-born veterinarian Jan Pol, his family and employees&apos; everyday. Jan Pol and his wife Diane started their own practice in Weidman, Michigan, Pol Veterinary Services, back in in 1981. Dr Pol takes a good care of every family pet and head of livestock no matter what size or condition and is a true legend in the community. Dr Pol has seen it all, treating numerous patients every single day, his daily routine is more than 12 hours but nothing can stop him from being devoted to his patients.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220141500 +0000" stop="20241220150000 +0000" channel="NationalGeographicWild.ee"><title lang="ee">The Incredible Dr. Pol</title><desc lang="ee">Reality show follows Dutch-born veterinarian Jan Pol, his family and employees&apos; everyday. Jan Pol and his wife Diane started their own practice in Weidman, Michigan, Pol Veterinary Services, back in in 1981. Dr Pol takes a good care of every family pet and head of livestock no matter what size or condition and is a true legend in the community. Dr Pol has seen it all, treating numerous patients every single day, his daily routine is more than 12 hours but nothing can stop him from being devoted to his patients.</desc></programme>
