<programme start="20241220090500 +0000" stop="20241220093000 +0000" channel="NickJr.ee"><title lang="ee">The Adventures of Paddington</title><desc lang="ee">Animated series about the classic children&apos;s character. Paddington is a charming young bear that has come from deepest, darkest Peru to live with the Brown family in London. Now that England is his home, there are a lot of new things for this curious bear to learn and Paddington&apos;s inquisitive nature takes him on some exciting adventures. Paddington is a kind and friendly kind of guy who is always willing to help. And even though his efforts to lend a hand often result in chaos and mess, Paddington&apos;s heart is always in the right place. He will do anything for his friends and family – all he needs is a delicious marmalade sandwich to keep his energy up! Featuring the voices of Ben Whishaw and Morwenna Banks.</desc></programme>
