<programme start="20241221000500 +0000" stop="20241221003000 +0000" channel="NickJr.ee"><title lang="ee">Deer Squad</title><desc lang="ee">Animated children&apos;s series centering on four caring, young deer who help animals and humans that share their world. The four young deer are comprised of Kai, Lola, Rammy and Bobbi, together they use their &quot;Planet Powers&quot; to assist anyone in need of help, whether it&apos;s the animals of Central Forest or the humans of Platinum City. Their magical woodland home is surrounded by the futuristic metropolis and the lovable deer are happy to help anyone in trouble. Their Planet Powers refer to the elements, with each deer summoning their own special attribute; Kai (water), Lola (wood), Rammy (sun), and Bobbi (earth).</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221003000 +0000" stop="20241221005000 +0000" channel="NickJr.ee"><title lang="ee">The Adventures of Paddington</title><desc lang="ee">Animated series about the classic children&apos;s character. Paddington is a charming young bear that has come from deepest, darkest Peru to live with the Brown family in London. Now that England is his home, there are a lot of new things for this curious bear to learn and Paddington&apos;s inquisitive nature takes him on some exciting adventures. Paddington is a kind and friendly kind of guy who is always willing to help. And even though his efforts to lend a hand often result in chaos and mess, Paddington&apos;s heart is always in the right place. He will do anything for his friends and family – all he needs is a delicious marmalade sandwich to keep his energy up! Featuring the voices of Ben Whishaw and Morwenna Banks.</desc></programme>
