<programme start="20241220063000 +0000" stop="20241220065500 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">The Loud House</title><desc lang="ee">In this crowded and chaotic household, Lincoln Loud is the only boy among his ten sisters. With eleven children under one roof, things get a little bit crazy sometimes, to say the least. This children&apos;s cartoon is fun and light-hearted, and Clyde, Lincoln&apos;s best friend, only adds to that. Clyde is an only child by contrast, and is jealous of Lincoln&apos;s abundance of siblings. Clyde also has a massive crush on Lori, who is Lincoln&apos;s oldest sister. However, she has a boyfriend, Bobby. Bobby, although not being particularly intelligent, has several different jobs, ranging from life guard, to security at a shopping centre.</desc></programme>
