<programme start="20241220182500 +0000" stop="20241220185000 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">The Casagrandes</title><desc lang="ee">Family-orientated cartoon for kids. Ronnie Anne Santiago, her big brother Bobby and their mum have recently moved to Great Lakes City and are now getting used to life in this busy, and sometimes chaotic, new town. Here in the big city they meet the Casagrandes – their extended family made up of grandparents, aunt, uncle, cousins and their pets. Along with a bunch of friends they all live as one big happy family. Skateboarding Ronnie Anne also starts to explore what their new hometown has to offer. Meanwhile, Bobby helps his grandfather Hector working in the family store where they meet lots of interesting characters from the neighbourhood.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220185000 +0000" stop="20241220191500 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">The Fairly OddParents</title><desc lang="ee">The Fairly OddParents tells us a story of Timmy Turner, a 10-year-old boy in the fictional town of Dimmsdale. Vicky is his babysitter with vicious temper. His parents are completely indifferent to him. His life is very sad and hopeless until his fairy godparents Wanda and Cosmo apperar in the fishbowl and try to fulfill his every wish. Timmy&apos;s greenness in making his wishes causes troubles and he has to &quot;unwish&quot; them together with his fairy godparents to avoid possible disasters. Enjoy Timmy&apos;s fantastic adventures in the world of fairies, dragons, unicorns and dwarfs.</desc></programme>
