<programme start="20241220222000 +0000" stop="20241220223000 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">The Penguins of Madagascar</title><desc lang="ee">The Penguins of Madagascar is an American animated television series, a spin-off of the Madagascar films. The main characters are penguins-commandoes: Skipper, Rico, Kowalski, and Private. They pretend to be white and fluffy but in reality are fearless adrenaline addicts and a secret spy team on a mission to protect their home in the Central Park Zoo. The penguins often have to deal with problems caused by their zoo lemur neighbors- King Julien XIII, Maurice and Mort. The penguins thwart any attempts of King Julien XIII to wield the sceptre of the Zoo.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220223000 +0000" stop="20241220225500 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">The Penguins of Madagascar</title><desc lang="ee">Antics on Ice: Private&apos;s in heaven - icy, freezing heaven. The Lunacorns on Ice extravaganza is in town, and Skipper&apos;s determined to take him as a treat. Accompanied by unexpected fellow fanboys Bing and Roy, the gang heads to the arena. Things get a bit d-icey when the gorilla and rhino end up on the ice with the lunacorns. The enraged director is ready to shutter the whole thing unless they find some way to slip &apos;n slide out of it. Showdown on Fairway 18:A legendary putter is at the center of controversy when the Amarillo Kid returns to the zoo. The slippery armadillo needs Private&apos;s help to make good on an ill-advised bet with two gopher brothers. Who&apos;s the bad guy here though? The gophers show up at the zoo to actually warn the penguins about the kid! The story takes us on more twists and turns than a Pebble Beach golf hole!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220225500 +0000" stop="20241220231500 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">The Penguins of Madagascar</title><desc lang="ee">King Me/Private and the Winky Factory King Me: King Julien&apos;s archrival, Clemson, returns in another attempt to claim the lemur crown. This time the sneaky lemur has a document that &quot;proves&quot; King Julien is not the legitimate king because he wasn&apos;t born in Madagascar. A series of challenges to prove who&apos;s more kingly ensues, and the penguins try to stack the deck in Julien&apos;s favor by each switching brains with him. Simple, right? How could a plan like this possibly fail? Private and the Winky Factory: Private&apos;s favorite treat, the Peanut Butter Winky, is going the way of the dinosaur. Distraught that the snack cake is ceasing production, Private urges a raid on the Winky Factory where the last remaining Winkies are rolling off the production line. Impressed by Private&apos;s passion, Skipper gives him command of the mission! The young penguin learns there&apos;s a heck of a lot to digest when leading a team. King Me: King Julien&apos;s archrival, Clemson, returns in another attempt to claim the lemur crown. This time the sneaky lemur has a document that &quot;proves&quot; King Julien is not the legitimate king because he wasn&apos;t born in Madagascar. A series of challenges to prove who&apos;s more kingly ensues, and the penguins try to stack the deck in Julien&apos;s favor by each switching brains with him. Simple, right? How could a plan like this possibly fail?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220231500 +0000" stop="20241220234000 +0000" channel="Nicktoons.ee"><title lang="ee">Avatar: The Last Airbender</title><desc lang="ee">Avatar: The Last Airbender is an American animated TV series, set in an Asiatic-like world. Some people there can manipulate the classical elements with psychokinetic variants of the Chinese martial arts. Unlike anybody else, 12-year-old Aang, the Avatar and last survivor of his nation, the Air Nomads, is capable of bending all four elements, his mission is to maintain harmony between the world&apos;s four nations. His flying bison Appa and friends Sokka, Katara, and later on Toph, are by his side on this challenging assignment.</desc></programme>
