<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="SetantaSports1.ee"><title lang="ee">LaLiga. Villarreal vs Real Betis</title><desc lang="ee">La Liga (The Campeonato Nacional de Liga de Primera División) is the men&apos;s top professional football division of the Spanish football league system. It is administered by the National Professional Football League and has 20 contestants, with the three lowest-placed teams at the end of each season relegated to the Segunda División and replaced by the top two teams and a play-off winner in that division. Nine teams have become champions, Real Madrid has got the title 33 times and FC Barcelona 26 times. La Liga is one of the most popular professional sports leagues in the world and the top league in Europe over the last five years.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220090000 +0000" channel="SetantaSports1.ee"><title lang="ee">Lega A. Virtus Segafredo Bologna vs Pallacanestro Trieste</title><desc lang="ee">The premier basketball league in Italy featuring top-tier professional teams and players.</desc></programme>
