<programme start="20241221043500 +0000" stop="20241221052600 +0000" channel="StarFamily.ua"><title lang="uk">Полет бабочки</title><desc lang="uk">В старом элитном доме селится молодая эффектная женщина Светлана с 10-летней дочкой Галей. Выясняется, что она сбежала из Парижа от своего бывшего французского мужа, который собирается отнять у нее дочку. У одного из соседей, известного антиквара Андрея Ковалевского, есть сын, ровесник Галочки. Дети быстро находят общий язык, что сближает их мам – Светлану и Ирину Ковалевскую. Вскоре Андрей, желая помочь несчастной соседке, берет ее на работу в свой антикварный салон. Это позволяет Светлане убедить суд оставить дочь при себе. Отношения Ковалевского и Светланы очень быстро переходят в романтическое русло, что сразу же понимает Ирина. Обычный любовный треугольник? Вовсе нет...</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220041500 +0000" stop="20241220051500 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Ruthless City</title><desc lang="lv">Seher starts working at Agah Bey&apos;s house with her children. Curious love triangles form between the children of the two families, and the terrible secrets in the mansion begin to be revealed.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220051500 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">When They Meet</title><desc lang="lv">The course of true love nevers runs smoothly. But what happens when your family don&apos;t approve of the person that you love and who you wish to marry? Join five couples as they face up to the challenges posed by their families&apos; prejudices and lack of support by agreeing to undergo professional therapy. In this way, they hope to be able to confront their parents, sister or best friend together to try to persuade them to change their minds.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220063500 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Family School</title><desc lang="lv">What are the current issues for families with children? The parents of two children - Dace and Jānis Siliņi - will study it, listening to the experiences of other new parents, as well as looking for answers to their own questions - how to balance everyday life with children, how to find and organize time together, how to organize rest with children, how to devote time only to yourself .</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220063500 +0000" stop="20241220074000 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Check in a Celebrity</title><desc lang="lv">Andris Bulis visits the popular people of Latvia. How do they actually live, what do they do, what are their daily lives and hobbies?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220074000 +0000" stop="20241220084000 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Below Deck Sailing Yacht</title><desc lang="lv">Captain Glenn confronts Jenna about her relationship with Adam and the way it has been distracting her from her duties. She doesn&apos;t make a good impression with her flat-out denials that she ever left just one person on service. What she seems to have forgotten is that he was there at the time. Meanwhile, a doctor visits and delivers bad news for Chris: he may have nerve damage. An MRI scan will be necessary to make sure, but if the damage is serious, this is an injury with the potential to end his sailing career. Later, Paget, who is already limping due to his own accident, injures his knee. With drama swirling in all departments, Glenn is shocked to learn that someone may have brought illegal drugs on to the boat. A tough decision and an impending drug search threaten to bring the charter season screeching to an early end. At least dinner works out well, with Adam producing an amazing meal at very short notice and winning a good deal of praise from the guests.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220084000 +0000" stop="20241220094000 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Below Deck Sailing Yacht</title><desc lang="lv">In the season finale, an uncomfortable drug search on the Parsifal III casts a dark cloud over the final charter and sends the crew into panic mode. Guest Billy, previously seen with white powder beneath his nose, has his luggage searched and is furious with Glenn. Madison makes a supreme effort to lighten the mood. The crew members scramble to pull together a sailing regatta which goes down really well, but they still wonder if they&apos;ll get a tip. Tensions in the interior department finally boil over, with a heated confrontation erupting. Georgia has feelings which she needs to get off her chest, even if that might mean altering some relationships forever. She&apos;s determined that before she leaves the yacht, Jenna will understand exactly what other crew members think about her behaviour. Captain Glenn takes the crew out one last time to celebrate Ciara&apos;s birthday and reminisce about the season. The crew says some final and emotional goodbyes.</desc></programme>
