<programme start="20241220213500 +0000" stop="20241220223500 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Desperate Housewives</title><desc lang="lv">Drama series is set on Wisteria Lane, a street in the fictional town of Fairview. Four housewives struggle through family life and its challenges, hiding their own problems and secrets behind a perfect picture. Susan Mayer is divorced and lives with her daughter, who seems to be more mature than her Mom. Gabrielle Solis is an ex-model, happily married to a businessman, she gets bored with family life and has an affair. Bree Van de Kamp is a strict principled perfectionist, whose son uses drugs, daughter has a new boyfriend every day. Lynette Scavo had to leave her beloved office and devote herself to taking care of four kids. Together the four women try to solve the mystery of suicide of the fifth housewife who has lived next to them and seemed to be so happy.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220223500 +0000" stop="20241220232500 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Desperate Housewives</title><desc lang="lv">Susan realises that Robin and Katherine are having a relationship. She tries to pay off Mike&apos;s business loan but he objects. Katherine seeks advice from Bob and Lee about her feelings for Robin. Gaby and Angie fly to New York to fetch Ana and Danny. Gaby realises that Ana is a much better model than she was after a chance encounter with Heidi Klum (making a cameo appearance). Preston returns from Europe with a Russian fiancée. And Bree finds out the truth about Sam.</desc></programme>
