<programme start="20241221000500 +0000" stop="20241221011500 +0000" channel="STVPirma.lv"><title lang="lv">Married at First Sight Australia</title><desc lang="lv">Flipping the traditional relationship model on its head, Married at First Sight is a social experiment and reality series that takes eight, single individuals and turns them into four married couples, meeting for the first time at the alter, before settling down and getting to know each other. The contestants are chosen out of thousands of applicants, with psychologist Sabina Read, neuropsychotherapist Dr. Trisha Stratford and physiologist John Aiken using science to formulate which couples will be the best match. Will they find true love at the hands of science? Or will their personalities clash too much?</desc></programme>
