<programme start="20241221032500 +0000" stop="20241221044000 +0000" channel="SuperPlus.lv"><title lang="ru">Дон Сезар де Базан</title><desc lang="ru">Испания XVIII век. Обедневший граф любит уличную танцовщицу, а она - его. Но их союзу противостоит самодовольный и беспринципный испанский король! Он положил глаз на прекрасную барышню и посадил несчастного графа в тюрьму. Дни узника сочтены... Однако настоящая любовь способна преодолеть и не такие преграды!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221044000 +0000" stop="20241221053500 +0000" channel="SuperPlus.lv"><title lang="ru">Семья и немного справедливости</title><desc lang="ru">Известная журналистка Марина Николаева, на похоронах звездного отца-генерала, узнает правду, к которой совсем не была готова - ее удочерили. Все вокруг, включая жениха Марины, Артема, твердят, что она стала жертвой нелепого розыгрыша. Но Марина не привыкла полагаться на домыслы - решает, во чтобы то ни стало, выяснить правду о своем истинном происхождении...</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220043000 +0000" stop="20241220050000 +0000" channel="TLC.ee"><title lang="ee">High Infidelity</title><desc lang="ee">How does a scorned lover react when their partner is revealed to be a traitor? This show re-enacts the betrayals, secrets and lies that lead couples to a breaking point.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220063200 +0000" channel="TLC.ee"><title lang="ee">90 Day Fiancé: Happily Ever After?</title><desc lang="ee">American reality series, a follow-up spinoff of &apos;&apos;90 Day Fiancé&apos;&apos; that features couples who have applied for or received a K-1 visa (available uniquely to foreign fiancés of U.S. citizens) and have ninety days to marry each other, follows some of the most famous and interesting couples from the original show and documents the ups and downs of their relationships after they got married. For some of these couples, the real drama is just starting because they barely know each other and they have to battle critics, doubters, and various obstacles on their road to love. Some of the couples that are featured on the show are Danielle and Mohamed, Melanie and Devar, Loren and Alexei, Kyle and Noon, Brett and Daya and Russ and Paola.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220063200 +0000" stop="20241220071900 +0000" channel="TLC.ee"><title lang="ee">Doubling Down With the Derricos</title><desc lang="ee">Meet Deon and Karen Derrico, mom and dad to 11 kids and with triplets on the way. Their days are pretty chaotic, and in this show, viewers have a chance to see everything - ups and downs, sleepless nights, all the drama but also all the love.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220071900 +0000" stop="20241220074200 +0000" channel="TLC.ee"><title lang="ee">Cake Boss</title><desc lang="ee">Carlo&apos;s Bakery in Hoboken New Jersey create elaborate, elegant and interesting edible art cakes. Cake Boss follows the team, led by Buddy Valastro, as they design and create two of these masterpieces for all kinds of events and occassions. The show explores the intricacy of working with your family, and their interpersonal relationships with other employees. Watch as they create everything from classic wedding cakes to alien spaceships.</desc></programme>
