<programme start="20241220091600 +0000" stop="20241220100300 +0000" channel="TLC.ee"><title lang="ee">Breaking Amish: Brave New World</title><desc lang="ee">Breaking Amish OGs, Abe, Rebecca, Sabrina, Jeremiah and Kate return in this follow up series to document the aftermath of their adventures in the Big Apple. Shunned and rejected for breaking away from their Amish roots, the group are struggling to reestablish their lives in isolation. With more culture shocks and surprises in store, they relocate to Sarasota Florida and join a large community of Amish and ex-Amish people and hope for a fresh start. Tensions rise and relationships intensify, as the group start to experience the backlash of leaving their families and everything they once knew behind. Now living life in the rays of the Florida sun, will they get burned?</desc></programme>
