<programme start="20241220130000 +0000" stop="20241220140000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Ghost Nation</title><desc lang="ee">Hair-rising American reality series that follows paranormal investigators Jason Hawes, Steve Gonsalves and Dave Tango, known from the &apos;&apos;Ghost Hunters&apos;&apos; television series, as they respond to calls from people who need their help with the cases of reportedly haunted locations around the United States. The guys are members of the paranormal investigation group- T.A.P.S., which Hawes founded, and they helped to create &apos;&apos;United Paranormal Research Organization (UPRO)&apos;&apos;, which aims to be a global paranormal investigation organization that keeps local organizations connected. Using state-of-the-art technology, strict methodology and local contacts, the team tracks down the source of the unexplained phenomena and cracks each outrageous case.</desc></programme>
