<programme start="20241220150000 +0000" stop="20241220160000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">The Holzer Files</title><desc lang="ee">Based on the real life files of America&apos;s first ghost hunter, Dr. Hans Holzer (whose most famous case concerned the Lutz family of Amityville, NY), this show follows a team of paranormal investigators as they reexamine the terrifying tales that mystified the doctor. The team consists of paranormal investigator Dave Schrader, psychic medium Cindy Kaza and equipment technician Shane Pittman and they are aided by Holzer&apos;s daughter, Alexandra. They examine thousands of documents, letters, photographs, and audio and visual recordings, sometimes going as far back as the 50s. Following on from where Holzer left off, the team bring the investigations up to the present day and visit the locations of the supernatural events such as the Peck House, the Morris-Jumel Mansion, the Whaley House, and the USS Constellation.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220160000 +0000" stop="20241220170000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">The Holzer Files</title><desc lang="ee">Based on the real life files of America&apos;s first ghost hunter, Dr. Hans Holzer (whose most famous case concerned the Lutz family of Amityville, NY), this show follows a team of paranormal investigators as they reexamine the terrifying tales that mystified the doctor. The team consists of paranormal investigator Dave Schrader, psychic medium Cindy Kaza and equipment technician Shane Pittman and they are aided by Holzer&apos;s daughter, Alexandra. They examine thousands of documents, letters, photographs, and audio and visual recordings, sometimes going as far back as the 50s. Following on from where Holzer left off, the team bring the investigations up to the present day and visit the locations of the supernatural events such as the Peck House, the Morris-Jumel Mansion, the Whaley House, and the USS Constellation.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220170000 +0000" stop="20241220180000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Kindred Spirits</title><desc lang="ee">Thrilling American paranormal docu-reality series that follows investigators Amy Bruni and Adam Berry who visit various haunted homes across the country in order to help people who are tormented by the spirits of their late relatives. These families are scared by the mysterious occurences and they will seek help from this amazing ghost-hunting duo. Amy and Adam will try to find evidence of paranormal presence, contact the spirits and provide closure for the featured family.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220180000 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Kindred Spirits</title><desc lang="ee">Thrilling American paranormal docu-reality series that follows investigators Amy Bruni and Adam Berry who visit various haunted homes across the country in order to help people who are tormented by the spirits of their late relatives. These families are scared by the mysterious occurences and they will seek help from this amazing ghost-hunting duo. Amy and Adam will try to find evidence of paranormal presence, contact the spirits and provide closure for the featured family.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220200000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Paranormal Lockdown</title><desc lang="ee">Two seasoned ghost hunters, Nick Groff and Katrina Weidman, present this reality show which investigates tales of the paranormal. In order to prove, or disprove, the presence of otherworldly souls, our two hosts spend 72 hours straight living alongside the spirits in some of the most haunted places in the US. By doing so, they believe that they will be contacted by the beings on the other side. From New York&apos;s darkly foreboding Wildwood Sanitarium to the eerily silent halls of Ohio&apos;s Higginsport School and the creepy Trans-Allegheny Lunatic Asylum in West Virginia, Nick and Katrina brave the chilling atmospheres to gather as much information as they can about the previous, long-departed occupants.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220200000 +0000" stop="20241220210000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">The Alaska Triangle</title><desc lang="ee">Experts and eyewitnesses attempt to unlock the mystery of the Alaska Triangle, a remote area infamous for alien abductions, Bigfoot sightings, paranormal phenomena and vanishing airplanes. Throughout the series, we meet a woman whose idyllic Alaskan dream soon descends into a paranormal nightmare, as she starts to suffer attacks by an unseen force. Recent sightings may prove that a Native American legend about a mysterious race of giants is true. The series also explores The Missing Douglas and whether an interdimensional portal in the Alaska Triangle led to the disappearance of the airplane carrying 44 military personnel in 1950.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220210000 +0000" stop="20241220220000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">The Ghost Town Terror</title><desc lang="ee">Tim uncovers a disturbing link between Gunslinger Gulch and a former brothel in Butte, Montana. Plus, an experiment at the ranch reveals a dark force&apos;s psychological warfare.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220220000 +0000" stop="20241220230000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Ghost Asylum</title><desc lang="ee">Featuring a fearless crew on a quest to hunt down chain-rattling ghosts and scary apparitions in anyway they can, Ghost Asylum follows a passionate paranormal team in America, the Tennessee Wraith Chasers (TWC) as they attempt to &quot;trap ghosts&quot; in the country&apos;s most haunted abandoned asylums, mental hospitals and sanitariums. Using their Sourthern charm and engineering knowledge to create supernatural inventions during their hunting to find ghosts or spirits of any kind. Their speciality is investigating the decaying, haunting and skin crawling mental institutions throughout the USA, warning viewers that they have permission to enter the most haunted buildings and that chasing ghosts without proper training &quot;will get you killed&quot;, so don&apos;t try this at home.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220230000 +0000" stop="20241221000000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">The Holzer Files</title><desc lang="ee">Based on the real life files of America&apos;s first ghost hunter, Dr. Hans Holzer (whose most famous case concerned the Lutz family of Amityville, NY), this show follows a team of paranormal investigators as they reexamine the terrifying tales that mystified the doctor. The team consists of paranormal investigator Dave Schrader, psychic medium Cindy Kaza and equipment technician Shane Pittman and they are aided by Holzer&apos;s daughter, Alexandra. They examine thousands of documents, letters, photographs, and audio and visual recordings, sometimes going as far back as the 50s. Following on from where Holzer left off, the team bring the investigations up to the present day and visit the locations of the supernatural events such as the Peck House, the Morris-Jumel Mansion, the Whaley House, and the USS Constellation.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221000000 +0000" stop="20241221010000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Kindred Spirits</title><desc lang="ee">Thrilling American paranormal docu-reality series that follows investigators Amy Bruni and Adam Berry who visit various haunted homes across the country in order to help people who are tormented by the spirits of their late relatives. These families are scared by the mysterious occurences and they will seek help from this amazing ghost-hunting duo. Amy and Adam will try to find evidence of paranormal presence, contact the spirits and provide closure for the featured family.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221010000 +0000" stop="20241221020000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Paranormal Emergency</title><desc lang="ee">Supernatural documentary series that features police officers, paramedics and other first responders who share their stories of interactions with mysterious entities while on duty. The viewers will have a chance to find out what happens when events they encounter on their jobs don&apos;t seem to coincide with the laws of the natural world. Each episode investigates various cases involving ghostly hauntings, demonic possessions, alien encounters and other &apos;&apos;bizarre&apos;&apos; emergency calls told through the eyes of the first responders.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221020000 +0000" stop="20241221030000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.ee"><title lang="ee">Ghosts Of Morgan City</title><desc lang="ee">After a Louisiana city struggles to deal with the sheer volume of emergency calls relating to encounters with creepy ghosts, Police Chief James Blair hires a team of paranormal experts to ascertain the truth behind these ghoulish happenings. Morgan City&apos;s residents have been left feeling terrified and tense after reports that ghosts from the city&apos;s past have started to haunt the bayou area. Comprised of Louisiana local Jereme Leonard, psychic medium Sarah Lemos, former FBI agent Ben Hansen, and local historian Diane Wiltz, the team delves into the truth behind the ghostly events. Reality-documentary series.</desc></programme>
