<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.lv"><title lang="lv">Legends Of The Lost With Megan Fox</title><desc lang="lv">Documentary series, hosted and co-created by actress Megan Fox, that follows her on an epic and personal journey across the world, where she will, with the help from archaeologists and experts, and analysing priceless texts and fascinating artifacts, try to find answers to the age-old mysteries that still torture scientists and archaeologists to this day. Among other themes, the series will consider whether female Amazon warriors really existed, whether the Trojan War was an historical event, and the mysteries of Stonehenge.</desc></programme>
