<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220080000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.lv"><title lang="lv">NASA&apos;s Unexplained Files</title><desc lang="lv">What do we really know about life beyond the realm of our planet? Disturbing discoveries about the rest of our universe have perplexed scientists, and the rest of the world, for as long as we can remember. Now, the files and discoveries of one of the worlds biggest independent agencies have been dug up, for thorough investigation. Each episode scrutinises questionable evidence, encounters and sightings, to shed some light on the unexplained files of NASA. Featuring testimonies of NASA insiders and scientists who have first hand experience of the enigmas, laying within our universe.</desc></programme>
