<programme start="20241220090000 +0000" stop="20241220100000 +0000" channel="TravelChannel.lv"><title lang="lv">Alien Highway</title><desc lang="lv">Thrilling documentary series that follows Chuck Zukowski, a former Colorado law enforcement officer, who has been researching and investigating UFO-related incidents for over 30 years, his son Daniel Zukowski and investigator Heather Taddy, as they search for proof of alien life, investigate reports of UFO-related incidents across America, trying to find evidence that others have missed, while listening to some of the witnesses that were afraid to come forward until now. The team will have many adventures- they will search for the infamous Skinwalker, go on a treasure hunt of a lifetime when they receive a mysterious map, attempt to find an alien that reportedly escaped from Area 51, investigate energy vortexes, and have many other paranormal and UFO-related activities.</desc></programme>
