<programme start="20241220043000 +0000" stop="20241220050000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.ee"><title lang="ee">Off the Grid</title><desc lang="ee">This exciting series takes you to some of the most unusual places all around the world. Join the presenters as they visit remote destinations that are not the typical choices for tourists. Off the Grid shows you the hidden and often overlooked places with all their treasures. Discover them through their culture, history and way of living. Explore the food, traditions and customs and meet the people of wonderful countries like Gabon, India, Ethiopia, Ireland and more.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220050000 +0000" stop="20241220053000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.ee"><title lang="ee">Food Fact Fun</title><desc lang="ee">Taking the visitor behind the scenes of well-known and popular tourist destinations, Food Fact Fun explores the cuisine and culture of cities the world over through a lively and adventurous look at the hidden side of culinary travel; shining some light on the facts and fun that can be learned and enjoyed while travelling in a culinary way through varied cultures and parts of the world.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220053000 +0000" stop="20241220060000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.ee"><title lang="ee">Quest</title><desc lang="ee">Take a chance to explore magnificent cities all around the world with the help of XP Guide with TravelXP. The hosts will walk you through the streets of cities in the four corners of the Earth, will introduce you to local cuisine, show you the night life, demonstrate modern and ancient architecture, provide the best shopping places. Even if you do not plan to visit this very city it will be absolutely entertaining and eye-opening experience. And if you get inspired by some particular place, do not forget to turn off TV before you go on the road.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220060000 +0000" stop="20241220063000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.ee"><title lang="ee">Xplore Sri Lanka</title><desc lang="ee">Documentary series. The beautiful diversity of Sri Lanka is laid bare for all to see in this exquisite travel show. A country encompassing more than 21 million inhabitants, Sri Lanka is know for it&apos;s gorgeous climate, pristine beaches and rich culture. With a focus on the country&apos;s history, the show explores the religious foundations of this ever-developing nation, and reveals just why it is so attractive to tourists. Nicknamed the &quot;teardrop of India&quot; this paradisaical island gem is home to some of our planet&apos;s most fascinating wildlife.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220063000 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.ee"><title lang="ee">World Heritage</title><desc lang="ee">Wonder the lengths of the globe learning all about the stories that made their homes in great kingdoms and unrivalled masterpieces, all from the comfort of your home with World Heritage. Whether its natural or man made, the interactions between the past and the present unlock a new angle from which we can observe these breathtaking sites and structures. Hosted by Travelxp, World Heritage aims to bring cutting edge travel content to travellers across the globe, bring the unseen and undiscovered into the forefront of the viewers&apos; mind. When it comes to Travelxp its all about the journey, your journey.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220073000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.ee"><title lang="ee">World Spas</title><desc lang="ee">Long work hours and stress definitely influence your mental and physical health. World Spas on Travelxp is a show for those who are ready to look after themselves and to relax by getting top treatments in a spa. Wrap yourself up in a soft bath robe, switch off your phone and enjoy to the fullest all wonders that a spa can offer, feel unique spiritual aura and energy. World Spas highlights the most exquisite spas in the world, where you can refresh and recharge your battery.</desc></programme>
