<programme start="20241220093000 +0000" stop="20241220100000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.lv"><title lang="lv">Backpack</title><desc lang="lv">For many years passion for travelling has been bringing people to unexplored continents, countries and places to look into culture, history, food, nature and people. This kind of passion if the key point of Backpack, a travel show that opens new spots all over the world by a show host travelling solo with a backpack. So make yourself comfortable and enjoy visiting Serbia, Spain, Israel, India, Egypt and many more. Take a look at the historical past and modern life, find out about traditions, get to know tourism hotspots and treasures of nature, plan your future vacations with the help of show hosts&apos; recommendations.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220100000 +0000" stop="20241220103000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.lv"><title lang="lv">Great World Hotels</title><desc lang="lv">Great World Hotels takes you on a journey to the some of the world&apos;s most luxurious hotels and resorts. We visit everything from your own personal lagoon island huts, the size of mansions, to the largest, most decadent penthouse in New York City. Live life like the stars as we explore every corner of the world from the comfort of your sofa. Season one alone takes us from Dubai to Mauritius to the Maldives. Whether you&apos;re an avid traveller or have never left the country, this journey is suitable for everyone. This is your journey. This is our journey.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220103000 +0000" stop="20241220110000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.lv"><title lang="lv">Off the Grid</title><desc lang="lv">This exciting series takes you to some of the most unusual places all around the world. Join the presenters as they visit remote destinations that are not the typical choices for tourists. Off the Grid shows you the hidden and often overlooked places with all their treasures. Discover them through their culture, history and way of living. Explore the food, traditions and customs and meet the people of wonderful countries like Gabon, India, Ethiopia, Ireland and more.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220110000 +0000" stop="20241220113000 +0000" channel="Travelxp.lv"><title lang="lv">Food Fact Fun</title><desc lang="lv">Taking the visitor behind the scenes of well-known and popular tourist destinations, Food Fact Fun explores the cuisine and culture of cities the world over through a lively and adventurous look at the hidden side of culinary travel; shining some light on the facts and fun that can be learned and enjoyed while travelling in a culinary way through varied cultures and parts of the world.</desc></programme>
