<programme start="20241220161500 +0000" stop="20241220171000 +0000" channel="ViasatExplore.ee"><title lang="ee">Aussie Lobster Hunters</title><desc lang="ee">Aussie Lobster Men is an Australian reality television series that revolves around the real events of crew on board commercial fishing vessels searching for Tasmanian rock lobsters around Tasmania. The crew work round the clock to get lobsters no matter what. Their enemies can be dreadful weather, medical emergencies, mechanical failures etc. Plus Lobster Men must keep a close eye on the price as it is volatile. Almost all lobsters caught in Tasmania are exported live to China and that&apos;s what drives the price. Will the captain get it right and make a fortune or will he find himself under huge financial pressure? Even if a single lobster is able to bring over $100, lobster fishing is not a banknote printing press, but a mixture of economics, pure luck, unthinkable fishing skills, back-breaking work and going an extra mile.</desc></programme>
