<programme start="20241221025000 +0000" stop="20241221034000 +0000" channel="ViasatHistory.ee"><title lang="ee">Cursed Treasures</title><desc lang="ee">One of the greatest palaeontology discoveries ever is made in the Hell Creek Formation of South Dakota, but the find brought nothing but trouble and suspicion to those who uncovered it.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221034000 +0000" stop="20241221042500 +0000" channel="ViasatHistory.ee"><title lang="ee">Strangest Things</title><desc lang="ee">The Stone Ball, The Electrocution Belt. A 5,000-year-old carved stone object is artfully shaped into four lobes covered in unique markings; who made it, and why did people believe that an electrocution device could cure people?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221042500 +0000" stop="20241221051500 +0000" channel="ViasatHistory.ee"><title lang="ee">Cursed Bloodlines</title><desc lang="ee">Documentary series that examines various family curses - the Kennedy Curse, the Grimaldi Curse, the Pharaoh Curse, the Getty Curse, the Mad Monk Curse,... and tells the true stories about famous families and their tragedies. These powerful families seemingly had it all, yet years of bad luck suggest that not even money or power could protect dynasties that are mentioned in this series. The documentary will try to answer if the source of their misfortune could be pride, wealth, genetics or something much more sinister.</desc></programme>
