<programme start="20241221032500 +0000" stop="20241221051000 +0000" channel="ViasatKino.lv"><title lang="lv">Charming the Hearts of Men</title><desc lang="lv">A romantic drama set during the politically charged early 60s where a sophisticated woman returns to her Southern home town and discovers her options are limited yet discrimination is plentiful. With the help of a Congressional ally, she inspires historic legislation which allows opportunities and protections never before afforded to women.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220043500 +0000" stop="20241220061000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Survivor</title><desc lang="ee">Milla Jovovich and Pierce Brosnan star in director James McTeigue&apos;s thriller. Kate Abbott (Jovovich) is an American diplomatic security officer working at the US embassy in London, where she vets visa applications to prevent potential terrorists from entering the States. But when she flags a suspicious Romanian (Roger Rees) to Bill Talbot (Robert Forster), who&apos;s high up in the Foreign Service, he unconvincingly dismisses her apprehension. However, it&apos;s clear that Kate&apos;s on to something when, shortly after expressing her concerns, she narrowly escapes death in a bomb blast that claims the lives of many of her colleagues. An unexpected turn of events causes the US and UK authorities to believe that Kate is in league with the terrorists, forcing her to go on the run, not only from her home and host governments, but also from a relentless assassin called the Watchmaker (Brosnan). Also starring James D&apos;Arcy, Angela Bassett, Dylan McDermott and Frances de la Tour.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220061000 +0000" stop="20241220075500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Fall</title><desc lang="ee">Stranded 2,000 feet at the top of a remote, abandoned radio tower, two expert climbers are put to the ultimate test as they desperately fight to survive the elements, a lack of supplies, and vertigo-inducing heights.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220075500 +0000" stop="20241220092500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Survivor</title><desc lang="ee">Milla Jovovich and Pierce Brosnan star in director James McTeigue&apos;s thriller. Kate Abbott (Jovovich) is an American diplomatic security officer working at the US embassy in London, where she vets visa applications to prevent potential terrorists from entering the States. But when she flags a suspicious Romanian (Roger Rees) to Bill Talbot (Robert Forster), who&apos;s high up in the Foreign Service, he unconvincingly dismisses her apprehension. However, it&apos;s clear that Kate&apos;s on to something when, shortly after expressing her concerns, she narrowly escapes death in a bomb blast that claims the lives of many of her colleagues. An unexpected turn of events causes the US and UK authorities to believe that Kate is in league with the terrorists, forcing her to go on the run, not only from her home and host governments, but also from a relentless assassin called the Watchmaker (Brosnan). Also starring James D&apos;Arcy, Angela Bassett, Dylan McDermott and Frances de la Tour.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220092500 +0000" stop="20241220110500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">The Legend of Hercules</title><desc lang="ee">The Legend of Hercules (2014) is a 3D action fantasy film directed by Renny Harlin and starring Kellan Lutz and Scott Adkins. In Ancient Greece circa 1300 B.C., Queen Alcmene prays to the gods to save the world from her tyrant husband King Amphitryon. The goddess Hera allows her husband Zeus to impregnate Alcemene so that she gives birth to a son who, according to prophecy, will restore peace on earth. When prince Hercules learns of his great destiny, he must make a choice - escape with his true love or fulfill his destiny and become a real hero.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220110500 +0000" stop="20241220124500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Fall</title><desc lang="ee">Stranded 2,000 feet at the top of a remote, abandoned radio tower, two expert climbers are put to the ultimate test as they desperately fight to survive the elements, a lack of supplies, and vertigo-inducing heights.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220124500 +0000" stop="20241220142000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Survivor</title><desc lang="ee">Milla Jovovich and Pierce Brosnan star in director James McTeigue&apos;s thriller. Kate Abbott (Jovovich) is an American diplomatic security officer working at the US embassy in London, where she vets visa applications to prevent potential terrorists from entering the States. But when she flags a suspicious Romanian (Roger Rees) to Bill Talbot (Robert Forster), who&apos;s high up in the Foreign Service, he unconvincingly dismisses her apprehension. However, it&apos;s clear that Kate&apos;s on to something when, shortly after expressing her concerns, she narrowly escapes death in a bomb blast that claims the lives of many of her colleagues. An unexpected turn of events causes the US and UK authorities to believe that Kate is in league with the terrorists, forcing her to go on the run, not only from her home and host governments, but also from a relentless assassin called the Watchmaker (Brosnan). Also starring James D&apos;Arcy, Angela Bassett, Dylan McDermott and Frances de la Tour.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220142000 +0000" stop="20241220155000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">47 Meters Down</title><desc lang="ee">Action thriller starring Mandy Moore and Claire Holt, directed by Johannes Roberts. Kate (Moore) is on holiday with her sister Lisa (Holt) in Mexico, to get over a broken heart. On a night out, the girls agree to go cage diving with two locals, Louis (Yani Gellman) and Benjamin (Santiago Segura). But the next morning on the boat, the sight of the shabby cage is not encouraging, and Lisa must persuade a nervous Kate to go through with it. After Louis and Benjamin go down and see an enormous shark, the girls are lowered in. Underwater, Lisa and Kate are entranced, but when the winch breaks, the cage, the girls and the entire winch mechanism plunge to the ocean floor. Fighting their terror, Kate and Lisa must find a way to get back to the boat with sharks circling above. Network premiere.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220155000 +0000" stop="20241220171500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">47 Metres Down: Uncaged</title><desc lang="ee">Four teenage girls go on a diving adventure to explore a submerged Mayan city in Mexico, but they soon face a battle for survival when they discover that the sunken ruins are home to a school of deadly great white sharks.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220171500 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">The New Daughter</title><desc lang="ee">Thriller starring Kevin Costner and Ivana Baquero. A single father moves his two children to rural South Carolina, only to watch his daughter exhibit increasingly strange behavior.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220204000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Grizzly Man</title><desc lang="ee">In this mesmerizing new film, acclaimed director Werner Herzog explores the life and death of amateur grizzly bear expert and wildlife preservationist Timothy Treadwell, who lived unarmed among grizzlies for 13 summers.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220204000 +0000" stop="20241220221000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">First Blood</title><desc lang="ee">Action-adventure. John Rambo - an ex-United States Special Forces soldier who fought in Vietnam and won the Congressional Medal of Honor - is a man who is still suffering from the memories of combat when he decides to visit a friend in Washington state. When he arrives in the small town of Hope, he is abused by the town&apos;s local sheriff, who sparks a violent outburst in Rambo that sees him thrown in jail. Rambo soon breaks free from imprisonment - and another bloody rampage could be imminent.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220221000 +0000" stop="20241220233000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Open Water</title><desc lang="ee">Based on a true story follows a young couple Daniel and Susan who are on an island holiday. Upon arrival at their hotel it becomes clear that Daniel and Susan&apos;s relationship is under strain from their workaholic lifestyles and they need a vacation even more than they realized. The next morning the loving and rested couple certified scuba divers board a local dive boat for an underwater tour of the reef. The boat is crowded with other vacationers and due to a series of innocent miscommunications and a distracted crew the couple is after only 40 minutes or so underwater accidentally left behind. What follows is the story of their ordeal: cold alone and miles from land the couple is adrift in shark-infested waters.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220233000 +0000" stop="20241221015000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Alpha Dog</title><desc lang="ee">Johnny Truelove is a drug dealer and son of a big-time criminal, who kidnaps Zach, the 15-year-old brother of hot-headed Jake Mazursky, who owes Johnny money. At first, Zach isn&apos;t scared, believing his brother would soon pay off his debt. Johnny is aided by his gang in the abduction and has his friend Frankie look after Zach. The form a strong brotherly bond, and Zach starts hanging out with his own captors.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221015000 +0000" stop="20241221034500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">Cryo</title><desc lang="ee">A riveting and mind-bending sci-fi thriller. Five scientists awaken from cryogenic sleep with amnesia in an underground facility, only to discover a killer stalking them.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221034500 +0000" stop="20241221052000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.ee"><title lang="ee">The Legend of Hercules</title><desc lang="ee">The Legend of Hercules (2014) is a 3D action fantasy film directed by Renny Harlin and starring Kellan Lutz and Scott Adkins. In Ancient Greece circa 1300 B.C., Queen Alcmene prays to the gods to save the world from her tyrant husband King Amphitryon. The goddess Hera allows her husband Zeus to impregnate Alcemene so that she gives birth to a son who, according to prophecy, will restore peace on earth. When prince Hercules learns of his great destiny, he must make a choice - escape with his true love or fulfill his destiny and become a real hero.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220043500 +0000" stop="20241220061000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">Survivor</title><desc lang="lv">Milla Jovovich and Pierce Brosnan star in director James McTeigue&apos;s thriller. Kate Abbott (Jovovich) is an American diplomatic security officer working at the US embassy in London, where she vets visa applications to prevent potential terrorists from entering the States. But when she flags a suspicious Romanian (Roger Rees) to Bill Talbot (Robert Forster), who&apos;s high up in the Foreign Service, he unconvincingly dismisses her apprehension. However, it&apos;s clear that Kate&apos;s on to something when, shortly after expressing her concerns, she narrowly escapes death in a bomb blast that claims the lives of many of her colleagues. An unexpected turn of events causes the US and UK authorities to believe that Kate is in league with the terrorists, forcing her to go on the run, not only from her home and host governments, but also from a relentless assassin called the Watchmaker (Brosnan). Also starring James D&apos;Arcy, Angela Bassett, Dylan McDermott and Frances de la Tour.</desc></programme>
