<programme start="20241220124500 +0000" stop="20241220142000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">Survivor</title><desc lang="lv">Milla Jovovich and Pierce Brosnan star in director James McTeigue&apos;s thriller. Kate Abbott (Jovovich) is an American diplomatic security officer working at the US embassy in London, where she vets visa applications to prevent potential terrorists from entering the States. But when she flags a suspicious Romanian (Roger Rees) to Bill Talbot (Robert Forster), who&apos;s high up in the Foreign Service, he unconvincingly dismisses her apprehension. However, it&apos;s clear that Kate&apos;s on to something when, shortly after expressing her concerns, she narrowly escapes death in a bomb blast that claims the lives of many of her colleagues. An unexpected turn of events causes the US and UK authorities to believe that Kate is in league with the terrorists, forcing her to go on the run, not only from her home and host governments, but also from a relentless assassin called the Watchmaker (Brosnan). Also starring James D&apos;Arcy, Angela Bassett, Dylan McDermott and Frances de la Tour.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220142000 +0000" stop="20241220155000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">47 Meters Down</title><desc lang="lv">Action thriller starring Mandy Moore and Claire Holt, directed by Johannes Roberts. Kate (Moore) is on holiday with her sister Lisa (Holt) in Mexico, to get over a broken heart. On a night out, the girls agree to go cage diving with two locals, Louis (Yani Gellman) and Benjamin (Santiago Segura). But the next morning on the boat, the sight of the shabby cage is not encouraging, and Lisa must persuade a nervous Kate to go through with it. After Louis and Benjamin go down and see an enormous shark, the girls are lowered in. Underwater, Lisa and Kate are entranced, but when the winch breaks, the cage, the girls and the entire winch mechanism plunge to the ocean floor. Fighting their terror, Kate and Lisa must find a way to get back to the boat with sharks circling above. Network premiere.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220155000 +0000" stop="20241220171500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">47 Metres Down: Uncaged</title><desc lang="lv">Four teenage girls go on a diving adventure to explore a submerged Mayan city in Mexico, but they soon face a battle for survival when they discover that the sunken ruins are home to a school of deadly great white sharks.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220171500 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">The New Daughter</title><desc lang="lv">Thriller starring Kevin Costner and Ivana Baquero. A single father moves his two children to rural South Carolina, only to watch his daughter exhibit increasingly strange behavior.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220204000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">Grizzly Man</title><desc lang="lv">In this mesmerizing new film, acclaimed director Werner Herzog explores the life and death of amateur grizzly bear expert and wildlife preservationist Timothy Treadwell, who lived unarmed among grizzlies for 13 summers.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220204000 +0000" stop="20241220221000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">First Blood</title><desc lang="lv">Action-adventure. John Rambo - an ex-United States Special Forces soldier who fought in Vietnam and won the Congressional Medal of Honor - is a man who is still suffering from the memories of combat when he decides to visit a friend in Washington state. When he arrives in the small town of Hope, he is abused by the town&apos;s local sheriff, who sparks a violent outburst in Rambo that sees him thrown in jail. Rambo soon breaks free from imprisonment - and another bloody rampage could be imminent.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220221000 +0000" stop="20241220233000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">Open Water</title><desc lang="lv">Based on a true story follows a young couple Daniel and Susan who are on an island holiday. Upon arrival at their hotel it becomes clear that Daniel and Susan&apos;s relationship is under strain from their workaholic lifestyles and they need a vacation even more than they realized. The next morning the loving and rested couple certified scuba divers board a local dive boat for an underwater tour of the reef. The boat is crowded with other vacationers and due to a series of innocent miscommunications and a distracted crew the couple is after only 40 minutes or so underwater accidentally left behind. What follows is the story of their ordeal: cold alone and miles from land the couple is adrift in shark-infested waters.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220233000 +0000" stop="20241221015000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">Alpha Dog</title><desc lang="lv">Johnny Truelove is a drug dealer and son of a big-time criminal, who kidnaps Zach, the 15-year-old brother of hot-headed Jake Mazursky, who owes Johnny money. At first, Zach isn&apos;t scared, believing his brother would soon pay off his debt. Johnny is aided by his gang in the abduction and has his friend Frankie look after Zach. The form a strong brotherly bond, and Zach starts hanging out with his own captors.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221015000 +0000" stop="20241221034500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">Cryo</title><desc lang="lv">A riveting and mind-bending sci-fi thriller. Five scientists awaken from cryogenic sleep with amnesia in an underground facility, only to discover a killer stalking them.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221034500 +0000" stop="20241221052000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoAction.lv"><title lang="lv">The Legend of Hercules</title><desc lang="lv">The Legend of Hercules (2014) is a 3D action fantasy film directed by Renny Harlin and starring Kellan Lutz and Scott Adkins. In Ancient Greece circa 1300 B.C., Queen Alcmene prays to the gods to save the world from her tyrant husband King Amphitryon. The goddess Hera allows her husband Zeus to impregnate Alcemene so that she gives birth to a son who, according to prophecy, will restore peace on earth. When prince Hercules learns of his great destiny, he must make a choice - escape with his true love or fulfill his destiny and become a real hero.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220041500 +0000" stop="20241220055000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Babysitting</title><desc lang="ee">What was supposed to be a quiet night of babysitting turns into a complete chaos after a few of the babysitter&apos;s friends arrive.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220055000 +0000" stop="20241220073500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">The War with Grandpa</title><desc lang="ee">Robert De Niro, Uma Thurman and Oakes Fegley all star in this raucous family comedy directed by Tim Hill. After the death of his wife, Ed (De Niro) is left at a loose end, and it starts to show. When he manages to get himself involved in a bust-up at the grocery store, his daughter Sally (Thurman) convinces him to move into her family&apos;s home, where they can keep a closer eye on him. Little does he know what antics he&apos;s about to become a part of. Enraged at the idea of giving up his precious room for his less precious grandpa, middle-child Peter (Fegley) decides that this means war... prank war. But Ed isn&apos;t the type of man to just roll over and surrender, and he&apos;s got a few tricks of his own up his sleeve. In a series of escalating events, Peter and Ed do battle over ownership of the bedroom, embroiling friends, family, and reptiles in their turf war along the way. When attempted negotiations fall through and a dodgeball showdown ends with a tie, it seems as if this grandson and grandpa may be destined to butt heads forever. Also featuring Christopher Walken and Rob Riggle. Network Premiere.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220073500 +0000" stop="20241220091500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Austin Powers: International Man of Mystery</title><desc lang="ee">A secret agent volunteers to be frozen in time in 1967, only to be revived 30 years later when his perennial foe, Dr Evil, threatens world domination. But the spy finds things very different to what he left. Stars Mike Myers.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220091500 +0000" stop="20241220113000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Where the Heart Is</title><desc lang="ee">The boyfriend of a pregnant teenager (Natalie Portman) leaves her broke and abandoned in Oklahoma, where she begins living secretly at Wal-Mart.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220113000 +0000" stop="20241220132000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Super Crazy</title><desc lang="ee">A woman in her 40s feels stuck in a routine with her career and her love life. She decides to change things a bit, but the ritual she tries has consequences that will turn her life upside-down.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220132000 +0000" stop="20241220151000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Blades of Glory</title><desc lang="ee">(2007) 93 mins 12 Comedy starring Will Ferrell, Jon Heder, Will Arnett and Amy Poehler, directed by Will Speck and Josh Gordon. Champion figure skater Chazz Michael Michaels (Ferrell) is a self-proclaimed sex addict, hard drinker and all-round bad boy from the streets of Detroit. His rival is Jimmy MacElroy (Heder) - the son of a billionaire, adopted for his exceptional athletic abilities, whose talent has been nurtured (and financed) ever since. When the two skaters are jointly awarded gold at the World Figure Skating Championship, a fight breaks out between them which results in both being barred from single men&apos;s figure skating for life. The years pass and the two are stuck in unfulfilling jobs, but then, encouraged by a diehard fan to return to competitive skating, Jimmy finds a loophole in the rules that means he might skate once again - in the pair&apos;s division. But who can possibly match Jimmy&apos;s skill, talent and determination to be a champion?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220151000 +0000" stop="20241220170500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Win a Date with Tad Hamilton!</title><desc lang="ee">Famous Hollywood actor Tad Hamilton (soap opera star Josh Duhamel making his film debut) is trying to promote his new movie. His manager (Sean Hayes) and his agent (Nathan Lane) both convince him to participate in a dating contest in order to improve his bad-boy image. The contest is won by Rosalee Futch (Kate Bosworth), an attractive young checkout girl who works at a Piggly Wiggly in West Virginia. When Tad ends up falling in love with her, he&apos;s willing to give up big-city life and move to small-town America. Meanwhile, her best friend and co-worker Pete (Topher Grace) is finally motivated to reveal his secret crush on her. Rosalee finds herself in the middle of a love triangle between her closest friend and a dream date.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220170500 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">New in Town</title><desc lang="ee">(2009) Renée Zellweger and Harry Connick Jr star in this romantic comedy from Danish director Jonas Elmer. Ambitous food company executive Lucy Hill (Zellweger) is in two minds when she&apos;s assigned to &quot;streamline&quot; an underperforming factory in snowbound Minnesota. On the one hand it definitely offers the opportunity for another promotion, while on the other she&apos;ll have to abandon her beloved, and warm, Miami. But ambition wins out, and it&apos;s not long before she&apos;s in New Ulm, where she gets a frosty reception from the locals, who unsurprisingly aren&apos;t happy that she&apos;s arrived to make a number of them redundant. It&apos;s not just the general unfriendliness that she must bear, she also has to deal with single parent Ted Mitchell (Connick Jr), the union boss who&apos;s out to save as many of the plant&apos;s employees as possible. They don&apos;t get off to a great start, but as time goes by their attitudes do begin to thaw... Edited for language. First screening on E4.&lt;br /&gt;</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220205000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">The One I Love</title><desc lang="ee">On the brink of separation, Ethan and Sophie (Mark Duplass and Elisabeth Moss) escape to a beautiful vacation house for a weekend getaway in an attempt to save their marriage. What begins as a romantic and fun retreat soon becomes surreal when an unexpected discovery forces the two to examine themselves, their relationship, and their future.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220205000 +0000" stop="20241220233000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">The Boat That Rocked</title><desc lang="ee">Comedy centered around a band of eccentric DJs running a rock &apos;n&apos; roll radio station from a boat on the North Sea. It&apos;s the swinging 60s, but mainstream broadcasters haven&apos;t caught up with the rise of rock &apos;n&apos; roll and pop music. With no one else playing the music that they want to listen to, the DJs decide to take matters into their own hands by starting a pirate radio station from their boat. A rousing success, they help a generation fall in love with these new kinds of music, much to the dismay of a government minister who strongly believes that this brash upstart culture has no place in British society.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220233000 +0000" stop="20241221011500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Blades of Glory</title><desc lang="ee">(2007) 93 mins 12 Comedy starring Will Ferrell, Jon Heder, Will Arnett and Amy Poehler, directed by Will Speck and Josh Gordon. Champion figure skater Chazz Michael Michaels (Ferrell) is a self-proclaimed sex addict, hard drinker and all-round bad boy from the streets of Detroit. His rival is Jimmy MacElroy (Heder) - the son of a billionaire, adopted for his exceptional athletic abilities, whose talent has been nurtured (and financed) ever since. When the two skaters are jointly awarded gold at the World Figure Skating Championship, a fight breaks out between them which results in both being barred from single men&apos;s figure skating for life. The years pass and the two are stuck in unfulfilling jobs, but then, encouraged by a diehard fan to return to competitive skating, Jimmy finds a loophole in the rules that means he might skate once again - in the pair&apos;s division. But who can possibly match Jimmy&apos;s skill, talent and determination to be a champion?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221011500 +0000" stop="20241221030000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain</title><desc lang="ee">Recorded at the world famous Madison Square Garden, Hart once again spits out funny anecdotes, great catchphrases, and tackles what man all too often struggles with - women and relationships! Uncut!</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221030000 +0000" stop="20241221044000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">Family Heist</title><desc lang="ee">Comedy. French comedy, produced in 2017. Carol is an introverted software engineer specialist, living still with her mother. Caroline is a brash thief hanging out in luxury hotels in the French Riviera. The two women don&apos;t know they are sisters.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221044000 +0000" stop="20241221062000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoComedy.ee"><title lang="ee">The Wedding Date</title><desc lang="ee">In this sparkling romantic comedy, Debra Messing plays Kat, a never-married New Yorker, who is invited to her parents&apos; London home for her younger sister&apos;s wedding. In a desperate attempt to face the ordeal with dignity, Kat hires Nick (Dermot Mulroney), a charming and handsome professional male escort, to pose as her new boyfriend. Over the course of the weekend, Nick takes on the role of the bride&apos;s therapist, the father&apos;s ideal son-in-law, the groom&apos;s new best friend and the object of every woman&apos;s affection. For Kat, what starts out as a pretend relationship with Nick begins to turn into something entirely unexpected: a second chance at love.</desc></programme>
