<programme start="20241220034000 +0000" stop="20241220052000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">The Ash Lad: In the Hall of the Mountain King</title><desc lang="ee">Fairy tale. Aspen, nicknamed Nothing Use, sets out with his two older brothers to rescue a princess from the hands of the Mountain King, a nasty troll. With the money from the reward they can rebuild their farm, which has been burned down due to the negligence of Espen. It will be a journey full of dangers and special encounters.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220052000 +0000" stop="20241220070000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">The Ash Lad: In Search of the Golden Castle</title><desc lang="ee">In the sequel to &apos;The Ash Lad&apos;, Espen and Kristin embark on a dangerous journey to save Espen&apos;s brothers, the kingdom, and perhaps the entire world.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220070000 +0000" stop="20241220085000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Night Train to Lisbon</title><desc lang="ee">Drama based on Pascal Mercier&apos;s bestseller. A desperate young woman and an intriguing book send staid Swiss professor Raimund Gregorius on a sudden quest to Portugal. Seeking the author, Raimund encounters mystery instead. He gradually pieces together decades-old secrets from people who, in their youth, united against the cruel Salazar dictatorship.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220085000 +0000" stop="20241220103500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Finding Your Feet</title><desc lang="ee">(2017) 111mins 12A Comedy starring Imelda Staunton as a posh woman who goes to live with her sister on a London housing estate after discovering that her husband has been having an affair with her best friend. At a grand soiree given in her honour, Lady Sandra Abbott (Staunton) discovers that her husband, Mike (John Sessions), has been having an affair with her best friend, Pamela (Josie Lawrence). Justifiably outraged, she leaves him. But where for? The only person she can think of staying with is her sister, Bif (Celia Imrie), who lives on a London housing estate. The sisters couldn&apos;t be more different, but when Bif invites Sandra to her dance class, things start to change. Will two sisters rediscover the relationship they had when they were kids? Could &quot;her majesty&quot; find happiness so late in life? And even end up living on a barge? Hope so! The ensemble cast of great British talent also includes Timothy Spall and Joanna Lumley. First Play on Film4.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220103500 +0000" stop="20241220121500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Ogre</title><desc lang="ee">Terrible events are worrying the inhabitants of the Morvan. Jules, a child who has recently arrived in the village, senses something sinister near his house.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220121500 +0000" stop="20241220134500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">In Harmony</title><desc lang="ee">Marc is an equestrian stuntman. After a traumatic injury, he loses all hope of ever getting back on a horse. Florence works for an insurance company and is in charge of Marc&apos;s case.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220134500 +0000" stop="20241220151500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Piece Montee / The Wedding Cake</title><desc lang="ee">Families gather together for a happy day - the wedding of their children - but it&apos;s also the time to reveal all their secrets.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220151500 +0000" stop="20241220165000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Starving Generation</title><desc lang="ee">At the age of 21, Zoe, who has quit her studies, moves into a roommate. After yet another low-paying job, the young woman decides to rebel. She writes a Charter of the hungry, a list of things that young people should no longer accept at work. Her goal is to attack the system from the inside by leading a collective fight, to think bigger, but above all to think together...</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220165000 +0000" stop="20241220190000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Brideshead Revisited</title><desc lang="ee">Adaptation of Evelyn Waugh&apos;s classic novel about a sensitive Oxford undergraduate. Middle-class student Charles Ryder befriends the flamboyant alcoholic Lord Sebastian Flyte, who takes him to visit his grand ancestral home. Charles is enthralled by Brideshead and Sebastian&apos;s family, the Marchmains - particularly his elegant sister Julia. Will their growing attraction destroy Charles&apos;s friendship with Sebastian, or will his loyalty to his drunken friend end his association with the Marchmains?</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220190000 +0000" stop="20241220203500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Chloe</title><desc lang="ee">Suspecting her husband of infidelity, gynecologist Dr. Catherine Stewart hires an escort named Chloe in order to test his faithfulness. Soon, the relationships between all three intensify.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220203500 +0000" stop="20241220220500 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">With or Without You</title><desc lang="ee">(1998) 90 mins 18 Michael Winterbottom&apos;s romantic drama stars Christopher Eccleston and Dervla Kirwan as married couple Vincent and Rosie Boyd whose attempts to have a baby are overshadowed when her old pen-pal Benoit (Yvan Attal) arrives from France and shows no sign of moving on. Distracted and jealous, Vincent seeks solace in the arms of an old flame of his own...</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220220500 +0000" stop="20241220235000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Food of Love</title><desc lang="ee">A group of ex-university students reunite to perform a Shakespeare play in a quaint English village.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220235000 +0000" stop="20241221013000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">A Clever Crook</title><desc lang="ee">Beffrois, a disillusioned police captain nearing retirement, has his curiosity aroused by a new art theft. Seemingly an art specialist, the burglar prefers works of average value. No doubt to avoid attracting attention. Another distinctive sign: he always passes by the roof. For Beffrois the investigation looks to be athletic. Direction, screenplay: Lucas Bernard (France, 2017)</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221013000 +0000" stop="20241221033000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">City of Tiny Lights</title><desc lang="ee">Crime drama. Private detective Tommy Akhtar takes on the case of a missing prostitute and finds himself drawn into the London underworld. Soon, he is involved in a web of intrigue, money and corruption that reconnects him with his own childhood and the things he has lost.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241221033000 +0000" stop="20241221052000 +0000" channel="ViasatKinoWorld.ee"><title lang="ee">Night Train to Lisbon</title><desc lang="ee">Drama based on Pascal Mercier&apos;s bestseller. A desperate young woman and an intriguing book send staid Swiss professor Raimund Gregorius on a sudden quest to Portugal. Seeking the author, Raimund encounters mystery instead. He gradually pieces together decades-old secrets from people who, in their youth, united against the cruel Salazar dictatorship.</desc></programme>
<programme start="20241220045000 +0000" stop="20241220054000 +0000" channel="ViasatNature.ee"><title lang="ee">The Yorkshire Vet</title><desc lang="ee">A heartwarming documentary series that follows the work of former Herriot Trainee Peter Wright and his partner. The show focuses on the declining veterinary specialism of small animals or livestock, and follows the pair of vets on visit to clients in remote farm locations as they care for animals in the rural communities of North Yorkshire. The show also benefits from the beautiful backgrounds and stunning scenery of the Yorkshire Dales and North York Moors, adding an extra dimension to this veterinary show.</desc></programme>
