<programme start="20241220123000 +0000" stop="20241220132000 +0000" channel="ViasatNature.ee"><title lang="ee">Wildest Survival</title><desc lang="ee">Dive into the breathtaking world of nature as we explore the lives of our planet&apos;s weirdest and wildest creatures, learning how they have adapted to their surroundings in order to survive. Some of these remarkable species have lived on our planet for thousands, if not millions, of years. We reveal how these animals have evolved through the generations to remain a thriving species. With the current, devastating environmental plight, Wildest Survival showcases the importance of these wonderful species, showing what we could lose if human habits remain unaltered.</desc></programme>
